eveloped specifically for hair and skin care applications.','Aculyn 28 Polymer, Acrylates/C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer, Acrilates/ C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer; Acrylates/ C10-30 Acrylates Crosspolymer','Keep from freezing; material may coagulate. The minimum recommended storage temperature for these materials is 1øC/34øF. The maximum recommended storage temperature is 49øC/120øF. These materials may coagulate if exposed to temperature outside this range. The coagulation process is irreversible.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"474 lb. Steel Drum\",\"474 lb. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Solvents\",\"acrylates & methacrylates\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 9 Months from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: >100oC\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: 58.08 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:54','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(7425,'ACRYLATES/C10-30 ALKYL ACRYLATE CROSSPOLYMER','100075','GCC','176429-87-1','1','acrylatesc10-30-alkyl-acrylate-crosspolymer','Fluffy white powder with a slight acetic odor.',NULL,'A film forming agent that\'s used as a thickener and stabilizer in cosmetic products. Mainly used in clear gels and liquids, as well as some sunscreens and facial scrubs. It-s typically designed to keep dispersions mixed in water from lumping. Commonly in sunscreen, facial moisturizer/lotion, anti-aging treatment, eye cream, exfoliant/scrub, cleanser, hair dye and styling gel.','Acrylates/C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer, Acrylates/ C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer; Acrylates/ C10-30 Acrylates Crosspolymer','Keep container tightly closed. Keep container in a cool, well-ventilated area.','[\"50 lb. Box\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Acrylates & methacrylates\",\"thickeners\",\"emulsifiers\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher S