l Ultrez 21, Acrylates/C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer, Acrylates/ C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer','In the dry form, Carbopol Ultrez 21 polymer is stable for a long period of time. Keep the containers tightly closed to prevent moisture pickup.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"22 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"44 lb. Box\",\"1 lb. Box\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Acrylates & methacrylates\",\"thickeners\",\"emulsifiers\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 200oF (93oC)\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:54','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(7428,'ACRYLATES/C10-30 ALKYL ACRYLATE CROSSPOLYMER','100078','GCC','176429-87-1','1','acrylatesc10-30-alkyl-acrylate-crosspolymer-3','White powder with a slight typical odor',NULL,'Is an acrylic acid polymer. It is an emulsion stabilizer, viscosity enhancer for aqueous solutions with high electrolyte tolerance and a thickener for mild (low active) personal cleansing formulations. Tego- Carbomer 341 ER is suitable for the preparation and stabilization of creams, lotions and suspensions.','Tego Carbomer 341 ER; Acrylates/C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer','Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area. Keep containers tightly closed when not in use.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emulsifier\",\"stabilizer\",\"foam & viscosity booster\",\"thickener\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:54','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(7429,'ACRYLATES/C10-30 ALKYL ACRYLATE CROSSPOLYMER','100079','GCC','176429-87-1','1','acrylatesc10-30-alkyl-acrylate-crosspolymer-4','QC: WHITE POWDER',