ell-ventilated place.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"20 kg. Drum\",\"50 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"cosmetics\"]','[\"Acidulants\"]','C4H6N4O3','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 230-234\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 230 \\u00f8C (dec.)(lit.)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 471.5 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:54','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(7465,'ALLANTOIN USP [DSM]','100115','GCC','97-59-6','1','allantoin-usp-dsm','White to off-white crystalline powder.',NULL,'Allantoin is considered to be nontoxic, nonirritating and non-allergenic. It has become desirable to various cosmetic and pharmaceutical applications as it enhances their efficacy by its action as a skin protectant. Allantoin is used in cosmetic lotions, creams, suntan products, scalp preparations, shampoos, lipsticks, and various aerosol preparations. It has also been used in various hygiene preparations such as toothpaste, mouthwash, eye drops, ear drops. As a moisturizer allantoin replenishes the soft and supple feeling to the skin. Allantoin is used in the topical pharmaceutical market in psoriasis medications and analgesic gels. It is approved by the FDA for the treatment of cold sores and fever blisters. This odorless white powder is derived by the oxidation of uric acid. It does not contain any material or ingredients of animal or human origin and does not come in contact with materials of animal or human origin during the manufacturing process.','Allantoin USP [DSM], Ureidohydantoin, Unichem Alt 2, 5-Doixo-4-Imidazolidinyl Urea','Store in a cool place. Keep container tightly closed in a dry and well-ventilated place.','[\"250 GramHDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 lb. HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 kg. HDPE OH Pail\",\"25 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"20 kg. Box\",\"50 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"25 kg. Box\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"cosmetics\"]','[\"Botanicals\",\"moisturizer\"]','C4H6N4O3','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 230-234\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 230 \\u00f8C (dec.)(lit.)\",\"API: YES\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: 300.44 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:54','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(7466,'ALL TRANS RETINOIC ACID USP POWDER','100116','GCC','302-79-4','1','all-trans-retinoic-acid-usp-powder','Yellow to orange crystalline powder with a floral odor.',NULL,'It is a drug commonly used to treat acne vulgaris and keratosis pilaris. Available as a cream or gel, it is also used to treat acute promyelocytic leukemia. It can stimulate skin growth and keep epidermic normal. It can slow down skin aging process for solarization, remove tiny wrinkles. It can reduce skin roughness.','Vitamin A Acid; Retinoic Acid; Tretinoin1; all-transVitamin A1 Acid; all-(E)-Retinoic Acid; all-trans-á- Retinoic Acid; Retin A2','Store away from UV light, air, and oxidizing agents. It is recommended to use all the powder immediately after opening the ampule. Any unused portion should be protected by an atmosphere of inert gas and protected from light.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Acidulants\"]','C20H28O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date if stored at -20oC\",\"Freight Classification: N\\/A\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 350.6 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 180-182\\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 283.88 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:54','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(7467,'ALMOND OIL BITTER NATURAL','100117','GCC','100-52-7','1','almond-oil-bitter-natural','Colorless to pale yellow liquid with a bitter almond odor.',NULL,'Used externally as a fragrance ingredient, bitter almond oil is sometimes an ingredient in moisturizers or lotions for the face as well as 