ublished studies of the long term effects of taking DHEA, particularly in the large doses used by athletes, or of its possible interactions with other agents.','Dehydroepiandrosterone [DHEA], Unihydag DH, Trans-Dehydroandrosterone; Dehydroepiandrosterone; Dehydroisoandrosterone; Pasterone','Keep container tightly closed in a dry, cool, well-ventilated area. Keep away from oxidizing materials.','[\"25 Gram Poly Bag\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"1 kg. Bag\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Nutritional supplements\"]','C19H28O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 182.1 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 146-15oC\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 288.42 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:54','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8333,'DEHYDROXANTHAN GUM','100984','GCC','11138-66-2','1','dehydroxanthan-gum','Off-white powder',NULL,'Multi-functional, it serves as both the fixative and the thickener/suspending agent for gels and other styling aids. Provides unprecedented hold under highly humid conditions without being tacky or flaking.','Dehydroxanthan Gum; Unitek AP; Xanthan Gum; Amaze XT','Keep in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area away from open flames, hot surfaces and sources of ignition. Protect from moisture.','[\"1 kg. HDPE WM Bottle\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Thickeners\",\"stabilizers\",\"gums\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: N\\/A\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:54','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8334,'DENATONIUM BENZOATE','100985','GCC','3734-33-6','1','denatonium-benzoate','COLORLESS LIQUID WITH AN EXTREMELY BITTER TASTE, ODORLESS',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'[null]','[\"Auto&transp.\"]','[null]',NULL,'[nul