er sensitizer than imidazolidinyl area for people sensitive or allergic to formaldehyde.','Germall II, Diazolidinyl Urea; Unimol II; N-(1,3-Bis(hydroxymethyl)-2,5-dioxo-4-imidazolidinyl)-N,N’-bis(hydroxymethyl)-urea; Imidazolidinylurea11; MicrocideIvtm','Store in a tightly closed container. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area away from incompatible substances.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"250 Gram Bottle\",\"5 kg. HDPE OH Pail\",\"40 lb. Pail\",\"20 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"50 kg. Drum\",\"500 lb. Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Preservatives\\/antimicrobials\"]','C8H14N4O7','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 264.60 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 278.22 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8364,'DIAZOLIDINYL UREA (AND) IODOPROPYNYL BUTYLCARBAMATE','101015','GCC','78491-02-8','1','diazolidinyl-urea-and-iodopropynyl-butylcarbamate','White odorless powder',NULL,'Diazolidinyl Urea, when combined in synergy with Iodopropoynyl Butylcarbamate, simply increase the effectiveness of Diazolidinyl Urea on its own as a skin moisturizer. Alows greater natural moisture.','Germall Plus Powder; Diazolidinyl Urea (and) Iodopropynyl Butylcarbamate; Unimol PP; N-(1,3-Bis(hydroxymethyl)-2,5-dioxo-4-imidazolidinyl)-N,N’-bis(hydroxymethyl)-urea; Imidazolidinylurea11; MicrocideIvtm','Keep containers tightly closed when not in use. Store in a cool, dry place, out of direct sunlight. Hygroscopic Material. Keep containers closed tightly when not in use.','[\"25 Gram Bottle\",\"50 Gram Bottle\",\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"20 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"50 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Preservatives\\/antimicrobials\"]','C8H14N4O7','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Class