late persists in the environment, and damages the hormone systems of animals. It is strongly suspected that humans eating these animals will be harmed as well.','Dibutyl Phthalate; Unitate DBP; n-Butyl Phthalate; Phthalic Acid Dibutyl Ester; DBP; 1,2-Benzenedicarboxylic Acid, Dibutyl Ester; Phthalic Acid, Dibutyl Ester','Keep container tightly closed in a dry and well-ventilated place. Containers which are opened must be carefully resealed and kept upright to prevent leakage.','[\"100 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"500 ml. Glass Bottle\",\"40 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"463 lb. Steel Drum\",\"480 lb. Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"plasticizers\",\"solvents\"]','C16H22O4','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 340 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: -35 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 278.34 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8368,'DICAPRYL ADIPATE','101020','GCC','108-63-4','1','dicapryl-adipate','Clear odorless liquid',NULL,'Is used as a low-temperature-resistant and low-viscosity plasticizer for PVC and its copolymers and cellulose esters e.g. cellulose acetate butyrate, and cellulose propionates. They are used as solvent carriers or coupling agents for polyurethane and photographic films.','Dicapryl Adipate; ALZO: Bernel Ester DCA, Dibasic Acid Ester; Hexanedioicacid,bis(1-methylheptyl) Ester; Adipicacidbis-(1-methyl-heptylester); Dioctan-2-yl Hexanedioate; Unipate DC','Keep container tightly closed in a dry and well-ventilated place. Containers which are opened must be carefully resealed and kept upright to prevent leakage.','[\"35 lb. Pail\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"plasticizers\",\"solvents\"]','C2H2Cl2O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: 