gin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: >230 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: -7.6 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 242.44 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8371,'DICETYLDIMONIUM CHLORIDE','101023','GCC','1812-53-9','1','dicetyldimonium-chloride','QC: CLEAR TO SLIGHTLY YELLOW LIQUID WITH ISOPROPANOL ODOR','Is a conditioning agent that is especially suitable for hair treatments. It contains isopropyl alcohol and is water-dispersible. Leaves hair feeling soft and smooth.',NULL,'SYN: VARISOFT 432CG',NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8372,'DICETYLDIMONIUM CHLORIDE','101024','GCC','1812-53-9','1','dicetyldimonium-chloride-1','QC: CLEAR, YELLOW LIQUID WITH SLIGHT CHARISTIC ODOR.','Is a conditioning agent that is especially suitable for hair treatments. It contains propylene glycol and is water-dispersible',NULL,'SYN: VARISOFT 432 PPG',NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8373,'DICHLOROETHYL ETHER','101025','GCC','111-44-4','1','dichloroethyl-ether','Clear to pale yellow liquid',NULL,'Selective solvent for production of high-grade lubricating oils, intermediate & cross-linker in organic synthesis. Reagent for organic synthesis; wetting and penetrating compound; spotting and dry cleaning scavenge lead deposits in gasoline. It is also used in the manufacture of medicinal and pharmaceutical oil solution sprayed on corn silks to control earworms.','Dichloroethyl Ether; Unitex DCEE; 1,1′-Oxybis(2-Chloro)Ethane; 1,5-dichloro-3-oxapentane; Sym-Dichloroethyl Ether; Beta,Beta’-Dichloroethyl Ether','Should be stored in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area in tightly sealed containers. Containers of dichloroethyl ether should be protected from physical damage and light, heat sparks, and open flames, and should be stored separately from strong oxidizers.','[null,null]','[\"Industrial\",\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Quarternary compounds\",\"solvents\"]','C4H8Cl2O','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 131 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: -47 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 143.01 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8374,'DICOCO QUAT','101026','GCC','61789-77-3,67-63-0','1','dicoco-quat','Clear yellow liquid',NULL,'Used in automatic car wash and rinse aid formulations as a superior cationic emulsifier to promote neading and rapid roll-of of rinse water.','Carspray 300; Dicoco Quat; Unispray 300','Store in original sealed containers at temperatures between 20oC and 25oC.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"177 kg. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Emulsifiers\",\"surfactants\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 50 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8375,'DICOCOYL PENTAERYTHRITYL DISTEARYL CITRATE (AND) SORBITAN SESQUIOLEATE (AND) CERA ALBA (AND) ALUMINUM STEARATES','101027','GCC','130328-22-2','1','dicocoyl-pentaerythrityl-distearyl-citrate-and-sor','QC: YELLOWISH WAX LIKE PELLETS, MP = 99 – 132 F',NULL,'W/O EMULSIFIER','SYN: DEHYMULS E, MIXTURE: DICOCOYL PENTAERYTHRITYL DISTEARATE CITRATE & SORBITAN SESQUIOLEATE & CERA ALBA (BEESWAX) & ALUMINUM STEARATE',NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8376,'DICOGEL','101028','GCC','NA','1','dicogel',NULL,NULL,'Is a derivative of phenylacetic acid, Dicogel has a pronounced anti-inflammatory, analgesic and mild antipyretic effect. Inhibits platelet aggregation. With prolonged use has a desensitizing effect. In rheumatic diseases, Dicogel reduces joint pain at rest and in motion, as well as morning stiffness and swelling of the joints, helps to increase range of motion; reduces post-traumatic and postoperative pain, and inflammatory edema.v','Dicogel','Keep protected from light at temperatures not above 25oC.','[null]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Acidulants\",\"active pharmaceutical ingredients\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 3 years from mfg date\",\"Freight Classification: N\\/A\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: YES\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8377,'DIETHANOLAMINE 99% TECH GRADE','101029','GCC','111-42-2','1','diethanolamine-99-tech-grade','Colorless to yellow viscous liquid',NULL,'DEA is used as a surfactant and a corrosion inhibitor. It is used to remove hydrogen sulfide and carbon dioxide from natural gas. In oil refineries, a DEA in water solution is commonly used to remove hydrogen sulfide from sour gas. It has an advantage over a similar amine ethanolamine in that a higher concentration may be used for the same corrosion potential. This allows refiners to scrub hydrogen sulfide at a lower circulating amine rate with less overall energy usage. DEA is a chemical feedstock used in the production of morpholine.','Diethanolamine 99% Tech Grade; Diethanolamine 99% REG Grade; UPAamate DEA; Unimine DEA; Di(2-hydroxyethyl)amine; 2,2′-Dihydroxydiethyamine; Diolamine; Bis(2-Hydroxyethyl)amine; 2,2′-Iminodiethanol','Keep in tightly closed containers, protect from mositure. Keep in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area, away from heat, sparks, and flames.','[\"45 lb. Blue OH Pail\",\"480 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Surfactants\",\"absorption bases\"]','C4H11NO2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 28\\u00f8C (82.40 \\u00f8F)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 105.14 g\\/mol-1\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8378,'DIETHANOLAMINE NF','101030','GCC','111-42-2','1','diethanolamine-nf','Clear colorless liquid',NULL,'Hydraulic fracturing fluid additive; Diethanolamine is a chemical that functions as a component in the production of lubricants for the textile industry, as a rubber chemicals intermediate, as a humectant and softening agent, as an emulsifier and dispersing agent in agricultural chemicals, cosmetics, and pharmaceuticals, as an ingredient in cutting oils, cleaners, polishers, and shampoos, as a gas conditioning agent, and as a chemical intermediate for morpholine, fatty acid salt emulsifiers, and alkyl sulfate salt emulsifiers.','Diethanolamine NF; DEA; Unimine DEA-N; Di(2-hydroxyethyl)amine; 2,2′-Dihydroxydiethyamine; Diolamine; Bis(2-Hydroxyethyl)amine; 2,2′-Iminodiethanol','Keep in a cool, dry place. Do not expose to direct sunlight.','[\"480 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"Industrial\"]','[\"Surfactants\",\"absorption bases\"]','C4H11NO2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 28\\u00f8C (82.40 \\u00f8F)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 105.14 g\\/mol-1\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8379,'DIETHYLENE GLYCOL','101031','GCC','111-46-6','1','diethylene-glycol','Colorless practically odorless liquid',NULL,'Diethylene glycol is used in the manufacture of unsaturated polyester resins, polyurethanes, and plasticizers. DEG is used as a building block in organic synthesis, e.g. of morpholine and 1,4-dioxane. It is a solvent for nitrocellulose, resins, dyes, oils, and other organic compounds. It is a humectant for tobacco, cork, printing ink, and glue. It is also a component in brake fluid, lubricants, wallpaper strippers, artificial fog solutions, and heating/cooking fuel. In personal care products (e.g. skin cream and lotions, deodorants), DEG is often replaced by selected diethylene glycol ethers. A dilute solution of diethylene glycol can also be used as a cryoprotectant; however, ethylene glycol is much more commonly used. Most ethylene glycol antifreeze contains a few percent diethylene glycol, present as an inadvertent byproduct of ethylene glycol production.','Diethylene Glycol; T/N: Unilene DEG; Ethanol, 2-2′-Oxybis; 2-(2-Hydroxyethoxy)ethanol; 3-Oxa-1,5-pentanediol; Brecolane NDG; Bis(beta-hydroxyethyl) ether','Container must be sealed tightly and kept in a dry, well-ventilated space. Avoid moisture.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"40 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"500 lb. Steel Drum\",\"520 lb. Drum\",\"520 lb. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\",\"Industrial\",\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Solvents\"]','C4H10O3','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 143.3\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: -10.45 \\u00f8C (13.19 \\u00f8F)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 106.12 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8380,'DIETHYLENE GLYCOL','101032','GCC','111-46-6','1','diethylene-glycol-1','QC: CLEAR COLORLESS LIQUID',NULL,NULL,'SYN: HEXAMETHYLDISILOXANE, DM-FLUID 0.65 CS, VOLASIL DM 0.65',NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8381,'DIETHYLENE GLYCOL DIBENZOATE','101033','GCC','120-55-8','1','diethylene-glycol-dibenzoate',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'[null]','[\"Chem.proc.\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8382,'DIETHYLENE GLYCOL DIBENZOATE AND DIPROPYLENE GLYCOL DIBENZOATE','101034','GCC','120-55-8, 2713