ow viscosity with high spreading properties and has good solvency for crystalline actives. It is a unique emollient that is especially suitable for light and non-oily skin care and sun care products.','TEGOSOFT- DEC is a unique emollient especially suitable for light and non-oily skin care and sun care products. TEGOSOFT DEC is an oil with low viscosity, high spreading properties and good solvency for crystalline actives.','Tegosoft DEC; Diethyl Carbonate; Unisoft DEC; Bis (2-Ethylhexyl) Carbonat; Bis (2-Ethylhexyl) Ester Carbonic Acid; Ethylhexyl Carbonate','Store in a cool, well-ventilated area.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"18 kg. Pail\",\"180 kg. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"oils\"]','C11H22O3','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: >200\\u00f8F (93\\u00f8C)\",\"Melting Point: > 1000\\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 202.29 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8386,'DIETHYLHEXYL CARBONATE, POLYGLYCERYL-4 LAURATE, PHENOXYETHANOL, DILAURYL CITRATE, BUTYLPARABEN, ETHYLPARABEN, PROPYLPARABEN, ISOBUTYLPARABEN','101038','GCC','14858-73-2, Mixture','1','diethylhexyl-carbonate-polyglyceryl-4-laurate-phen','Clear liquid with characteristic odor',NULL,'Tegowipe is a ready to use, PEG-free concentrate for cosmetic wet wipes. It is cold processable and can be used to create facial, body and baby care wet wipes and O/W sprays and lotions. Has excellent makeup removing properties and provides a light, non-oily feeling on the skin.','Tego- Wipe DE PF; Unowipe DE; Diethylhexyl Carbonate, Polyglyceryl-4 Laurate, Phenoxyethanol, Dilauryl Citrate','Store in original container, away from light, heat and moisture at temperatures above 77øF (25øC).','[\"100 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"200 kg. Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emulsifiers\",\"preservatives\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 3 years from mfg. date when properly stored\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8387,'DIETHYLHEXYLCYCLOHEXANE','101039','GCC','100182-46-5','1','diethylhexylcyclohexane','Clear colorless oily liquid',NULL,'A medium spreading emollient which is hydrolysis stable and particularly suitable for all formulations where a wide pH range is needed e.g. deo/antiperspirant and hair remover formulations.','Cetiol S; Dioctyl Cyclohexane; Unitol S; 1,3 Di-octyl cyclohexane; Cyclohexane, 1,3-bis(2-ethylhexyl)-; Cyclohexane, diisooctyl-; Dioctylcyclohexane; 1,3-Bis(2-ethylhexyl)cyclohexane; 1,3-dioctylcyclohexane','Protect from moisture at below 30ø C. Store in a well-ventilated area.','[\"35 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"385 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"oils\"]','C22H44','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 182.2\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 308.58 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8388,'DIETHYL PHTHALATE FRAG GRADE','101040','GCC','84-66-2','1','diethyl-phthalate-frag-grade','Colorless oily liquid',NULL,'Is a suitable solvent for many organic molecules, it is often used to bind cosmetics and fragrances. Other industrial uses include plasticizers, detergent bases and aerosol sprays. Because of the frequent dermal exposure of humans to the chemical, the question of toxicity is crucial. Several studies suggest that DEP can cause damage to the nervous system as well as to the reproductive organs in males and females.','Diethyl Phthalate Grag Grade; Uniflex DEP; Anozol; Amozol;PHTHALOL; Neantine; Solvanol; NSC 8905; Estol1550; Placidole; Unimollda; Estol 1550','Store in cool place. Keep container tightly closed in a dry and well-ventilated place. Containers which are opened must be carefully resealed and kept upright to prevent leakage.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"40 lb. Steel Pail\",\"496 lb. Steel Drum\",\"225 kg. Steel Drum\",\"225 kg. Poly Drum\",\"500 lb. Steel Drum\",\"518 lb. Drum\",\"530 lb. St Blk Drum\",\"250 kg. Steel Drum\",\"250 kg. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\",\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Plasticizers\",\"emollient & esters\",\"acidulants\"]','C12H14O4','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 161.1 \\u00f8C (322.0 \\u00f8F)\",\"Melting Point: -40.5 \\u00f8C (-40.9 \\u00f8F)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 222.24 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8389,'DIGLYCEROL','101041','GCC','627-82-7','1','diglycerol','Colorless to yellowish, odorless viscous liquid',NULL,'It is a mild humectant, provides gloss to hair and can enhance fragrance/flavor impact and longevity. It also provides advantages in formulation design.','Diglycerol; Diglycerin; Diglycerine; 3,31-Oxybis-1,2-Propanediol; Oxybis-Propanediol;Oxydi(Propanediol);Tetrahydroxydi-N-Propyl Ether3-glyceryloxypropane-1,2-diol;3-(2,3-dihydroxypropoxy)propane-1,2-diol','Store in original container in a well-ventilated place. Keep cool.','[\"250 kg. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Solvents\"]','C6H14O5','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 200 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 166.17 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8390,'DIGLYCERYL ADIPATE/CAPRATE/CA