t. Is an intermediate used in the production of dyes, lubrification oils, corrosion inhibitor, detergents and cutting fluids. It can neutralize pH, act as a buffer (stabilize pH), or add basicity (alkalinity) to a solution. Because diisopropanolamine is a good solubilizer of oil and fat, it is\r\nfrequently used to neutralize fatty acids and sulfonic acidbased surfactants.','Diisopropanolamine 99%; T/N: Unichem DIPA; Unamine D99; DIPA NF; Dipa(alcohol); IminodiPropanol; Diisopropanolamin; Bis(2-propanol)Amine','Keep in well-ventilated place and free from exposure on sunshine and raining.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"40 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"450 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Emulsifiers\",\"stabilizers\",\"buffering agents\",\"surfactants\"]','C6H15NO2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 260 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: 42-45 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 133.19 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8398,'DIISOPROPYL ADIPATE','101050','GCC','6938-94-9','1','diisopropyl-adipate','Clear, colorless liquid with faint characteristic odor',NULL,'Is used as an emollient in cosmetics and as a plasticiser.','Diisopropyl Adipate; Upamate DIPA; Adipic acid, Diisopropyl Ester; Crodamol DA; Iso-adipate 2/043700; Standamul DIPA','Containers should be kept tightly closed and stored in a dry well-ventilated place.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"7 lb. HDPE NM Jug\",\"35 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"40 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"440 lb. St Blk Drum\",\"450 lb. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\",\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"plasticizer\"]','C12H22O4','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 109.8 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: -1.10 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 230.30 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8399,'DIISOPROPYL ADIPATE','101051','GCC','6938-94-9','1','diisopropyl-adipate-1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8400,'DIISOPROPYL SEBACATE','101052','GCC','2042106','1','diisopropyl-sebacate','Clear, colorless liquid',NULL,'JEECHEM DIS demonstrates excellent compatibility in hydro-alcoholic cosmetic formulations. Typical uses for JEECHEM DIS in hydro-alcoholic products are special face lotions, where it functions as a non-oily emollient lubricant with mild drying effects. Aside from the superior mutual solvent and coupling agent properties, JEECHEM DIS is an outstanding cosmetic emollient with wide and fast spreading action, permitting its use in bath oils: frequently, in combination with mineral oil and other esters. Additionally, it is used in lip products, men-s grooming aids and hand lotions.','Diisopropyl Sebacate; dipropan-2-yl decanedioate;Di isopropyl Sebacate (DIPS);Schercemol Diisopropyl Sebacate; Decanedioicacid,bis(1-methylethyl)ester; decanedioicaciddiisopropylester; Schercemol DIS; Unipol SBT','Store in original containers keeping them securely sealed. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area. Store away from incompatible materials and foodstuff containers.','[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Acidulants\",\"plasticizer\",\"solvents\",\"emollient & esters\"]','C16H30O4','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: N\\/A\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 134.9\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 286.41 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8401,'DIISOSTEAROYL POLYGLYCERYL-3 DIMER DILINOLEATE','101053','GCC','187547-43-9','1','diisostearoyl-polyglyceryl-3-dimer-dilinoleate','Yellow liquid','PEG-free emulsifier based on vegetable raw material. Suitable for W/O creams and lotions with brilliant white appearance and pleasant application properties. Compatible with all kinds of cosmetic oils and commonly used active ingredients.','Is suitable for W/O creams and lotions with a brilliant white appearance and pleasant application properties. It is compatible with all kinds of cosmetic oils and commonly used as active ingredients.',NULL,'Keep in sealed, unopened, original containers at 60ø – 80ø F. Avoid conditions of high humidity and temperature.','[\"200 K Drum\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Vegetable- Rapeseed Oil\",\"Shelf life: Two years from manufacture date.\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8402,'DIMETHICONE','101054','GCC','63148-62-9 / 9006-65-9 / 9016-00-6','1','dimethicone','Clear, colorless, odorless, liquid',NULL,'Is a moisture barrier especially for skin care or skin protection formulations. It is a perfume and active substnce fixative; improves application properties. Also, it is non-sticky with good emollient properties. It has an elimination of whitening effect from O/W emulsions.v','Dimethicone; Siloxanesand Silicones, di-Me;B 8919;BX 16-152B;BY 222-067R;DA 6523; Dehesive 940A; Dehesive 942; Dicsilicone Softener 300; Dow Corning 3-4680; ECC 4865; Magnasoft HWS;Matsumoto Silicone Softener 318; RossilFluid; Polydimethylsiloxane; Unibil 350; Abil 350','Keep in sealed, unopened, original containers at 60-80oF. Avoid conditions of high humidity and temperature.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"50 kg. Drum\",\"200 kg. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"emulsifiers\",\"silicones\"]','C6H18OSi2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 3 years from mfg. date in unopened original packaging\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 250 \\u00f8C (482 \\u00f8F)\",\"Melting Point: >50\\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8403,'DIMETHICONE','101056','GCC','63148-62-9 / 9006-65-9 / 9016-00-6','1','dimethicone-1',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'USE REASONABLE CARE AND STORE AWAY FROM OXIDIZING MATERIALS','[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8404,'DIMETHICONE 30000 CST','101057','GCC','63148-62-9','1','dimethicone-30000-cst','Clear, colorless, odorless, tasteless liquid',NULL,'A form of silicone used to give products lubricity, slip, and good feel. It can also serve as a formulations de-foamer and help reduce the feeling of greasiness that some creams leave on the skin immediately upon application. It is also reported to protect the skin againstloisture loss when used in large quantities. Improves product flow and spreadability. Is a good waterproofing material for sunscreen emulsions, and helps reduce the greasiness often seen in high SPF preparations.','Dimethicone 30000 CST; GE SF 18-350; Siloxanesand Silicones, di-Me;B 8919;BX 16-152B;BY 222-067R;DA 6523; Dehesive 940A; Dehesive 942; Dicsilicone Softener 300; Dow Corning 3-4680; ECC 4865; Magnasoft HWS; Unicone 30','Keep in sealed, unopened, original containers at 60-80oF. Avoid conditions of high humidity and temperature.','[\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"emulsifiers\",\"silicones\"]','C6H18OSi2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 3 years from mfg. date in unopened original packaging\",\"Freight Classification: N\\/A\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 250 \\u00f8C (482 \\u00f8F)\",\"Melting Point: >50\\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8405,'DIMETHICONE','101058','GCC','63148-62-9 / 9006-65-9 / 9016-00-6','1','dimethicone-2','QC: CLEAR, COLORLESS LIQUID WITH SLIGHT ODOR.',NULL,NULL,'SYN: DC 1503 FLUID',NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8406,'DIMETHICONE','101059','GCC','63148-62-9 / 9006-65-9 / 9016-00-6','1','dimethicone-3','QC: CLEAR, COLORLESS, ODORLESS LIQUID',NULL,NULL,'SYN: DC 1413 FLUID',NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8407,'DIMETHICONE (AND) DIMETHICONOL','101060','GCC','9006-65-9','1','dimethicone-and-dimethiconol','QC: CLEAR COLORLESS LIQUID WITH MILD ODOR.',NULL,NULL,'SYN: DC 1403',NULL,'[null]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8408,'DIMETHICONE COPOLYOL','101061','GCC','64365-23-7','1','dimethicone-copolyol','Colorless to slightly hazy light yellow to amber liquid',NULL,'Is an easy-to-formulate product which may be used to impart the conditioning benefits of silicone to personal care products without contributing to greasiness or build-up that is normally associated with water-insoluble silicone fluids.','DC 190 [Dimethicone Copolyol], XIAMETER- OFX-0190 Fluid; Ethoxylated, Propoxylated Silicone Oil; Dimethylsiloxane, poly(oxyethylene oxypropylene) copolymer; Siloxanes and Silicones; Uncone DCP','Store in sealed containers at temperatures not exceeding 90øF (32øC).','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"40 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"441 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"emulsifiers\",\"silicones\",\"surfactants\"]','C6H18OSi2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 11\\/2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8409,'DIMETHICONE PEG 7 OLIVATE','101062','GCC','None','1','dimethicone-peg-7-olivate','Creamy white liquid',NULL,'Water dispersible nonionic conditioner and emollient derived from olive oil, it is designed for use in shampoos, body wash, and conditioners where it contributes gloss, combability, static reduction and manageability.','Dimethicone PEG 7 Olivate; Unisil DW-20; Unicone P7','No special instructions.','[\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"fatty acids\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 3 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC144920 CL65\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8410,'DIMETHICONE PEG-8 POLYACRYLATE','101063','GCC','217958-64-0','1','dimethicone-peg-8-polyacrylate','TAN OPAQUE LIQUID',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8411,'DIMETHICONE PROPYL PG-BETAINE','101064','GCC','146905-77-3','1','dimethicone-propyl-pg-betaine','Colorless to amber liquid','It is used as a conditioning agent for shampoos. It sofetns and smoothes hair while improving manageability.','Is a conditioning agent for damaged hair. The conditioning effect of ABIL B 9950 improves the combability and feel of hair. In conditioning shampoos ABIL- B 9950 in combination with cationic guar reduces the fading out of artificial dyes caused by shampooing (improved wash fastness). Furthermore combability, volume and antistatic effects are improved in combinations with cationic guar resp.','Dimethicone Propyl PG-Betaine; Unibil B9950; Abil B 9950; Siloxanesand Silicones; 3-[3-[(carboxymethyl)dimethylammonio]-2-hydroxypropoxy]propylMe; di-Me, inner salts','No special instructions.','[\"250 ml. Glass Bottle\",\"20 kg. Pail\",\"200 kg. Poyl Drum\",\"1 lb.Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"emulsifiers\",\"silicones\",\"surfactants\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8412,'DIMETHICONE SF-10','101065','GCC','63148-62-9','1','dimethicone-sf-10','Clear viscous liquid',NULL,'In cosmetics applications, the low viscosity of dimethicone makes the ingredient an extremely good spreading agent, which creates a non-tacky moisture barrier in skin creams and lotions. This fluid can also eliminate the whitening or -soaping- effect seen in W/O emulsions. Soluble in alcohols.','Dimethicone SF-10; Unicone SF10; Siloxanes and Silicones','Keep in sealed, unopened, original containers at 60-80oF. Avoid conditions of high humidity and temperature.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"40 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"420 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"emulsifiers\",\"silicones\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8413,'DIMETHICONE/VINYL DIMETHICONE CROSSPOLYMER','101066','GCC','243137-53-3','1','dimethiconevinyl-dimethicone-crosspolymer','QC: SOFT WHITE POWDER WITH SLIGHT ODOR.',NULL,NULL,'SYN: DC 9506 POWDER',NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8414,'DIMETHICONE / VINYL DIMETHICONE CROSSPOLYMER (AND) SILICA','101067','GCC','869736-22-1','1','dimethicone-vinyl-dimethicone-crosspolymer-and-sil','QC: FINE WHITE POWDER',NULL,NULL,'SYN: DC 9701 COSMETIC POWDER',NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8415,'DIMETHYL DIHYDROGENATED TALLOW AMMONIUM CHLORIDE','101068','GCC','61789-80-8','1','dimethyl-dihydrogenated-tallow-ammonium-chloride','Clear, colorless, liquid',NULL,'Base for hair conditioners and cream rinses. Has antistati properties in hair conditioners.','Adogen 442 (75%); Dimethyl Dihydrogenated Tallow Ammonium Chloride; Udogen 442-75; Quaternium-18; Varisoft 442-100P; Kemamine Q 9702','Store in cool place. Keep container tightly closed in a dry and well-ventilated place.','[\"250 ml. Bottle\",\"390 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Quarternary compounds\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 25oC\",\"Melting Point: 30-45oC\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8416,'DIMETHYLETHANOLAMINE','101069','GCC','108-01-0','1','dimethylethanolamine','Colorless liquid with fishy ammoniacal odor',NULL,'Dimethylaminoethanol is used as a curing agent for polyurethanes and epoxy resins. It is also used in mass quantities for water treatment, and to some extent in the coatings industry. It is used in the synthesis of dyestuffs, textile auxiliaries, pharmaceuticals, emulsifiers, and corrosion inhibitors. It is also an additive to paint removers, boiler water and amino resins.','Dimethylethanolamine; Unamine DYE; 2-(Dimethylamine) Ethanol; Amietol M 21; 2-dimethylamino-ethano','Store in a cool area with containers tightly sealed. Store away from oxidizing materials and protect from heat.','[\"1000 ml. Glass Bottle\",\"400 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\",\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Emulsifiers\",\"coating & sealants chemicals\"]','C4H11NO','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 5 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 105 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: -59\\u00f8C (-74.2 \\u00f8F)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 89.14 g\\/mol-1\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8417,'DIMETHYL ISOSORBIDE','101070','GCC','5306-85-4','1','dimethyl-isosorbide','Colorless transparent oily liquid',NULL,'Its particular skin pnetrating ability opens the possibility of enhancing active substance efficacy in optical products. Is a carrier.','Dimethyl Isosorbide; Unisolve DMI-20; 1,4:3,6-Dianhydro-2,5-di-O-methyl-D-glucitol, 1,4:3,6-Dianhydrosorbitol 2,5-dimethyl ether, 2,5-Di-O-methyl-1,4:3,6-dianhydro-D-glucitol, Dimethyl isosorbide','Keep container tightly closed in a dry and well-ventilated place. Containers which are opened must be carefully resealed and kept upright to prevent leakage.','[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Solvents\"]','C8H14O4','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: N\\/A\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 108.3 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: -70 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 174.20 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8418,'DIMETHYLSILOXANE, PROPYLENE OXIDE/ETHYLENE OXIDE BLOCK POLYMER','101073','GCC','68937-55-3','1','dimethylsiloxane-propylene-oxideethylene-oxide-blo','CLEAR-STRAW LIQUID WITH MILD ODOR',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8419,'DIOCIDE','101074','GCC','1117-86-8,122-99-6','1','diocide','White to slightly yellow clear liquid with characteristic odor',NULL,'Diocide is a 100% active, paraben-free, formaldehyde-free, broad spectrum anti-microbial for cosmetics and personal care products. This preservative is equally suitable for rinse-off and leave-on applications. Diocide is stable over a wide pH range, compatible with most cosmetic ingredients','Diocide; Unocide D; Diocid; Pyridinium, 1-hexadecyl-, bromide, mixture with chloro(2-hydroxyethyl)mercury; Cetylpyridinium bromide mixture with Hydroxyethylmercuric chloride','Store at room temperature (15 – 25§C) and protected from light.','[\"100 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Preservatives\\/antimicrobials\",\"emulsifiers\"]','C21H38NC2H5ClHgOBr','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 665.62 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8420,'DIOCTYL ADIPATE','101075','GCC','123-79-5','1','dioctyl-adipate','Colorless to yellowish liquid',NULL,'Is a plasticizer. DOA is a diester of adipic acid and two equivalents of n-octanol.','Dioctyl Adipate; T/N: Dermol DOA; Unipate DA; Bis(2-ethylhexyl)adipate; Di-(2-ethylhexyl)adipate; Adipic acid; Bis(2-ethylhexyl)ester','Keep only in original container, in a cool, dry, well ventilated place.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"420 lb. Steel Drum\",\"425 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Acidulants\",\"plasticizers\"]','C22H42O4','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: \\u00f219oC\",\"Melting Point: -7.48 \\u00f8C (18.54 \\u00f8F)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 370.57 g\\/mol-1\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8421,'DIOCTYL PHTHALATE','101076','GCC','117-81-7','1','dioctyl-phthalate','Colorless to pale yellow oily liquid',NULL,'DEHP is the most common of the class of phthalates which are used as plasticizers. Due to its suitable properties and the low cost, DEHP is widely used as a plasticizer in manufacturing of articles made of PVC. DEHP also finds use as a solvent in glowsticks.','Dioctyl Phthalate; Unoctyl DOP; Di-sec-octyl phthalate; DOP; Bis(2-Etheylexyl) Phthalate; Octoil; Ethyl hexyl phthalate; Octyl phthalate','Keep container tightly closed in a dry, cool, well-ventilated area.','[null]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Plasticizers\",\"solvents\",\"acidulants\"]','C24H38O4','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 405 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: -50 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 390.56 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8422,'DIPALMITOYLETHYL HYDROXYETHYLMONIUM METHOSULFATE','101077','GCC','161294-46-8','1','dipalmitoylethyl-hydroxyethylmonium-methosulfate','White soft paste',NULL,'This cationic emulsifier primarily works as an anti-static agent (fabric softener), and secondarily as a hair conditioning and detangling ingredient. It\'s known for helping to soften and moisturize the hair, and can also work as a wetting agent in cosmetic products.','Dipalmitoylethyl Hydroxyethylmonium Methosulfate; Unitox GA-90; Ammonyx GA-90; UNII-X241W7C3L7; Ethanaminium, N-(2-hydroxyethyl)-N-methyl-2-((1-oxohexadecyl)oxy)-N-(2-((1-oxohexadecyl)oxy)ethyl)-, methyl sulfate (Salt)','Store in original containers in a cool (below 30øC), dry, well ventilated area and out of direct sunlight.','[\"7 lb. HDPE NM Jug\",\"40 lb. HDPE TH Pail\",\"420 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\",\"Industrial\"]','[\"Emulsifiers\",\"quarternary compounds\",\"preservatives\\/antimicrobials\"]','C40H81NSO9','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 48580 SUB 3 CLASS 55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: 752.14 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8423,'DIPALMITOYL HYDROXYPROLINE','101078','GCC','41672-81-5','1','dipalmitoyl-hydroxyproline','QC: CREAM COLORED POWDER WITH CHARACTERISTIC ODOR',NULL,NULL,'SYN: SEPILIFT DPHP, DIPALMITOYL HYDROXYPROLINE,',NULL,'[null]','[\"Vitamin\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8424,'DIPHENHYDRAMINE HCL USP','101079','GCC','147-24-0','1','diphenhydramine-hcl-usp','White crystalline powder',NULL,'Diphenhydramine hydrochloride blocks the effect of histamine at Histamine H1 Receptor (H1 receptor) sites, which results in an increase in vascular smooth muscle contraction. Diphenhydramine hydrochloride has been shown to have inhibitive tumor promotion properties.','Diphenhydramine HCL USP; Diphenhydramine HCL; 2-benzhydryloxy-N,N-dimethylethanamine HCl; Unihymine H; DPH','Keep container tightly closed. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"50 Gram Bottle\",\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Active pharmaceutical ingredients\"]','C17H21NOHCl','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 101.5 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 168-172 \\u00f8C\",\"API: YES\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 291.82 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8425,'DIPOTASSIUM GLYCYRRHIZINATE POWDER','101080','GCC','68797-35-3','1','dipotassium-glycyrrhizinate-powder','White powder',NULL,'Is chiefly applied to pharmaceuticals industry as the material of eyedrop and officinal toothpaste. It has the efficacy in anti-inflammatory, antianaphylaxis and moist boost. It is active against conjunctivitis, keratitis, stomatitis and periodontitis. Is used for skin refresher lotion and facial cream in cosmetic industry. Also used as sweetening agent, antistaling agent and flavouring agent for sports drinks. It is also useful as an anti-inflammatory and co-emulsifier to treat skin disorders and in cosmetics.','Dipotassium Glycyrrhizinate PDR; Unamect GA; Dipotassium Salt of Glycyrrhizic Acid; Unipot DG; -D-Glucopyranosiduronic acid; (3-,20-)-20carboxy-11-oxo-30- norolean-12-en-3-yl 2-O—Dglucopyranuronosyl-, dipotassium salt (9 CI)','When not in use, tightly seal the container and store in a dry, cool place. Avoid excessive heat and light.','[\"25 Gram Poly Bag\",\"25 Gram Bottle\",\"50 Gram Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\",\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Sweetener\",\"emulsifiers\",\"flavors\"]','C42H60K2O16','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: 899.12 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8426,'DIPROPYLENE GLYCOL DIBENZONATE','101081','GCC','27138-31-4','1','dipropylene-glycol-dibenzonate','QC: CLEAR OFF WHITE OILY LIQUID WITH MILD ESTER ODOR',NULL,NULL,'SYN: BENZOFLEX 988, DIPROPYLENE GLYCOL DIBENZOATE',NULL,'[null]','[\"Chem.proc.\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8427,'DIPROPYLENE GLYCOL IND GRADE','101082','GCC','25265-71-8','1','dipropylene-glycol-ind-grade','Colorless liquid with characteristic odor','Dipropylene Glycol meets the requirements for personal care manufacturers in Europe. It is also used as a reactive intermediate in the manufacture of high performance unsaturated polyester resins, polyurethanes, and plasticizers. While DPG is similar to the other glycols, its greater solvency and higher viscosity also make it the best choice for hydraulic brake-fluid formulations, cutting oils, textile lubricants, and industrial soaps.','Dipropylene glycol finds many uses as a plasticizer, an intermediate in industrial chemical reactions, as a polymerization initiator or monomer, and as a solvent. Its low toxicity and solvent properties make it an ideal additive for perfumes and skin and hair care products. It is also a common ingredient in commercial fog fluid, used in entertainment industry fog machines.','Dipropylene Glycol IND Grade; Unilene DPG-I; 1,1′-OXYDI-2-Propanol; Oxydipropanol; Dipropylene glycol, 99%, mixture of isomeric propylene glycol ethers','Keep conta