 for neutral pH or mildly acidic conditions common to most food and pharmaceutical products.','Disodium EDTA [ NA2S ]; Dissolvine NA2-S, Universene 100; Disodium EDTA Dihydrate; Disodium EDTA; Cheladrate; Disodium ethylenediamine-N,N,N’,N’-tetraacetate; Selekton B 2','Keep container tightly closed in a dry, cool and well-ventilated place.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 lb. HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 kg. HDPE OH Pail\",\"25 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"50 lb. Bag\",\"50 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"25 kg. Bag\",\"55 lb. Bag\",\"55 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Food & bev.\",\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Chelating agents[sequestrants]\"]','C10H14N2Na2O8','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48581 S0 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 325.2\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 237-24oC\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 336.21 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8444,'DISODIUM GUANYLATE','101104','GCC','1333479','1','disodium-guanylate','White crystalline powder',NULL,'Disodium guanylate is produced from dried fish or dried seaweed and is often added to instant noodles, potato chips and other snacks, savoury rice, tinned vegetables, cured meats, and packaged soup.','Disodium Guanylate; 5′-Guanylicacid, disodium salt (7CI,8CI,9CI); Sodium guanylate; GMP sodium salt; Unisod DSG; Guanosine 5′-monophosphate disodium salt','Store in a well-closed container away from moisture. Store away from direct sun light.','[\"20 Gram Poly Bag\",\"10 kg. Tin\"]','[\"Food & bev.\"]','[\"Flavors\"]','C10H12N5Na2O8P','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 492.2\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 300 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 407.18 g\\/mol-1\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8445,'DISODIUM LAURETH SULFOSUCCINATE',