gh DMAE to maintain rather than improve brain function, and it is impossible to get enough DMAE from dietary sources to treat mental disorders.','DMAE Bitartrate Powder, DMAEB, Dimethylaminoehtanol; Bitartrate, DMAE Tartrate; Dimethylethylamine Bitartrate; Unitrate DMAE; Atrol; 2-Dimethylamino-Ethanotartrate; Dimethaen','Should be stored in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area in tightly sealed containers.','[\"25 Gram Poly Bag\",\"100 Gram Poly Bag\",\"5 kg. HDPE OH Pail\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Vitamins\",\"nutritional supplements\"]','C8H17NO7','[\"Origin: Natural\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 231.4 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 109-113 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 239.22 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8471,'D-MANDELIC ACID','101136','GCC','611-71-2','1','d-mandelic-acid','White to off-white crystalline powder',NULL,'Is a synthetic intermediate commonly used for pharmaceutical synthesis.','D-Mandelic Acid; Upadel MA100; (àR)-à-Hydroxybenzeneacetic Acid; D-Mandelic Acid; (-)-(R)-Mandelic Acid; D-2-Phenylglycolic Acid','Store in a cool, dry, well-ventialted area in tightly sealed containers.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"1 kg. Bottle\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Acidulants\",\"amino acids\"]','C8H8O3','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 170.1\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 130-13oC\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 152.2 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8472,'D-MANNITOL GRANULAR USP K','101137','GCC','69-65-8','1','d-mannitol-granular-usp-k','White crystalline granules','Used in the anticancer drug, antibacterial, antihistamine medicine, in vitamin,