eners\",\"emollient & esters\",\"acs\\/reagent\"]','C6H14O6','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 292.6\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 167-170 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 182.17 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8477,'DMDM HYDANTOIN','101142','GCC','6440-58-0','1','dmdm-hydantoin','Clear water-white liquid with characteristic odor',NULL,'DMDM hydantoin is an antimicrobial formaldehyde releaser preservative with the trade name Glydant. DMDM hydantoin is an organic compound belonging to a class of compounds known as hydantoins. It is used in the cosmetics industry and found in products like shampoos, hair conditioners, hair gels, Rite Aid Liquid Lubricant, and skin care products. DMDM hydantoin works as a preservative because the released formaldehyde makes the environment less favorable to the microorganisms.','DMDM Hydantoin; T/N: Jeecide DMDM Hydantoin; T/N: Lanodent DM; T/N: Protacide DMDM H; Uniguard DMDM; Dantion DMDMH; Dantoguard; Bis(hydroxymethyl)-5,5-dimethyl-2,4-imidazolidinedione; Unidant G','Keep container tightly closed. To maintain product quality, do not store in heat or direct sunlight. Keep in a dry, cool and well-ventilated place. Storage temperatureshould be > 15øC.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"40 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"25 kg. Pail\",\"200 kg. Steel Drum\",\"200 kg. Poly Drum\",\"441 lb. Steel Drum\",\"441 lb. Poly Drum\",\"500 lb. Poly Drum\",\"240 kg. Poly Drum\",\"530 lb. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Preservatives\\/antimicrobials\"]','C7H12N2O4','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: > 93\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 188.18 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8478,'DMDM HYDANTOIN (AND) IODOPROPYNYL BUTYLCARBAMATE GRANULAR','101144','GCC','6440-58-0','1','dmdm-hydantoin-and-iodopropynyl-butylcarbamate-gra','White granules',NULL,'Is a unique and cost effective preservative featuring a high level of antimicrobial activity in a wide variety of cosmetic and personal care formulations. It is also highly effective in inhibiting the growth of gram positive and gram negative bacteria, yeasts and mods without the need of additional auxiliary preservatives.','DMDM Hydantoin (and) Iodopropynyl Butylcarbamate Granular; Glydant Plus Granular; Unidant GP; DMDMH and IPBC; Dantogard(R) Plus','Keep container tightly closed. To maintain product quality, do not store in heat or direct sunlight. Store at room temperature in the original container.','[\"1 kg. Bottle\",\"40 lb. Steel Pail\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Preservatives\\/antimicrobials\"]','C7H12N2O4','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 306 \\u00f8F (152 \\u00f8C)\",\"Melting Point: 194 - 207 \\u00f8F (90 - 97 \\u00f8C)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 188.20 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8479,'DMDM HYDANTOIN (AND) IODOPROPYNYL BUTYLCARBAMATE LIQUID','101145','GCC','6440-58-0, 116-25-6','1','dmdm-hydantoin-and-iodopropynyl-butylcarbamate-liq','Clear viscous liquid',NULL,'Is a unique and cost effective preservative featuring a high level of antimicrobial activity in a wide variety of cosmetic and personal care formulations. It is also highly effective in inhibiting the growth of gram positive and gram negative bacteria, yeasts and mods without the need of additional auxiliary preservatives.','DMDM Hydantoin (and) Iodopropynyl Butylcarbamate Liquid; Glydant Plus Liquid; Unidant PL; DMDMH and IPBC; Dantogard(R) Plus','Keep container tightly closed. To main