-21-1','1','ethylene-glycol-industrial','Clear colorless liquid',NULL,'EG is primarily used as a raw material in the manufacture of polyester fibers and fabric industry, and polyethylene terephthalate resins (PET) used in bottling. A small percent is also used in other applications such as antifreeze formulations and other products.','Ethylene Glycol Industrial; Unichem EG-T; 1,2-Dihydroxyethane; 1,2-Ethanediol; Ethylene Alcohol; Lutrol-9; Norkool; Tescol; Ucar 17','Container must be sealed tightly and kept in a dry, well-ventilated space. Avoid moisture.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"510 lb. Steel Drum\",\"510 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Chemicals general\"]','C2H6O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 230 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: -13 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 62.07 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8538,'ETHYLENE GLYCOL MONOSTEARATE FLAKES','101208','GCC','111-60-4','1','ethylene-glycol-monostearate-flakes','White or cream colored flakes with characteristic odor',NULL,'A non-comedogenic raw material that provides a pearly look and consistency to clear preparations.','Ethylene Glycol Monostearate Flakes; Unichem EGMS; 2-Hydroxyethyl Stearate; Emalex EGS-A; Cerasynt M; Emerest 2350; Glycol monostearate; Glycol stearate','Store in cool dry place. Keep away from heat and incompatible materials.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"50 lb. Bag\",\"50 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"200 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"225 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emulsifiers\"]','C20H40O3','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC144920 CL65\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 164.6 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 55-60 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 328.53 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8539,'ETHYL HEXANOL','101209','GCC','104-76-7','1','ethyl-hexanol','Dark brown liquid with an aromatic odor','It is used as a raw material for plasticizers. It is also utilized in the production of acrylates, surfactants, defoamers, fuel additives, and lube additives.','Almost all 2-ethylhexanol is converted into the diesters bis(2-ethylhexyl) phthalate (DEHP), a plasticizer. Because it is a fatty alcohol, its esters tend to have emollient properties. For example, the sunscreen octocrylene contains a 2-ethylhexyl ester for this purpose. It is also commonly used as a low volatility solvent. 2-Ethylhexanol can also be used as an octane booster when reacted with nitric acid.','Ethyl Hexanol; Unityl EH; 2-Ethyl-1-hexanol; 1H-1,2,4-Triazole; 2-Ethylhexan-1-ol; 2-Ethylhexyl alcohol; Pyrrodiazole; s-Triazole','Keep away from heat, sparks, and flame. Keep away from sources of ignition. Keep container closed when not in use. Store in a tightly closed container. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area away from incompatible substances.','[\"376 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Fatty alcohols\",\"emollient & esters\",\"solvents\"]','C8H18O','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 5 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 171 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: -76 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 130.23 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8540,'ETHYLHEXYL PALMITATE (OCTYL PALMITATE)','101210','GCC','29806-73-3','1','ethylhexyl-palmitate-octyl-palmitate','Colorless to light yellow liquid','Is a universal oil with skin care properties and has good solubilizing properties for active ingredients.','Ethylhexyl palmitate is used in cosmetic formulations as a solvent, carrying agent, pigment wetting agent, fragrance fixative and emollient. Its dry-slip skinfeel is s