ielding pleasant application properties.',NULL,NULL,'Keep in sealed, unopened, original containers at 60ø – 80ø F. Avoid conditions of high humidity and temperature.','[\"250 G Bottle\",\"25 K Bag\",\"55 LB Drum\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Vegetable\",\"Shelf life: Two years from manufacture date.\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8712,'GLYCERYL STEARATE SELF EMULSIFYING','101397','GCC','11099-07-3, 593-29-3','1','glyceryl-stearate-self-emulsifying','White to off-white powder with mild faint fatty odor',NULL,'The anionic self-emulsifying base is suitable for the preparation of cosmetic O/W emulsions for skin and hair care.','Cutina GMS-SE; Glyceryl Stearate Self Emulsifying; Unitina GMS-SE','No special instructions.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 kg. Bag\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emulsifiers\",\"fatty acids\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC145020 CL65\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 56 - 61\\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8713,'GLYCERYL STEARATE & SODIUM LAURYL SULFATE','101398','GCC','Mixture','1','glyceryl-stearate-sodium-lauryl-sulfate','White powder or flakes',NULL,'Lexemul- AS is a self-emulsifying glyceryl monostearate designed for use as an emulsifier, stabilizer, opacifier, and emollient in anionic systems. Because it is acid stable, it can be used in acidic systems as low as pH 4-5 as well as alkaline systems. Lexemul- AS is recommended for use in most types of cosmetics, toiletries, and topical pharmaceutical preparations. It is particularly recommended for low pH anionic systems and systems that incorporate electrolytes.','Lexemul AS; Glyceryl Stearate & Sodium Lauryl Sulfate; Unimul AS','Store in a cool, dry, well ventilated place and out of direct sunlight. Store away from sources of