PEARL N 100',NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8725,'GLYCOL ETHER EB','101412','GCC','57-11-4','1','glycol-ether-eb','Colorless liquid with a mild, ether-like odor',NULL,'Glycol Ether EB is an excellent solvent and coalescent for solvent- and water-based paint, coating, ink and adhesive formulations. It has excellent solvency for a variety of resins including acrylic, alkyd, phenolic, epoxy, nitrocellulose and urethane resins. Glycol Ether EB is an important component in household and industrial cleaners, enhancing wetting and cleaning ability.','Glycol Ether EB; Unicol EB; Bucs; Monobutyl Ether Of Ethylene Glycol; Glycol Ether EB Acetate; O-Butyl Ethylene Glycol','Store only in tightly closed, properly vented containers away from heat, sparks, open flame or strong oxidizing agents.','[\"415 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Solvents\"]','C6H14O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 72 \\u00f8C (161 \\u00f8F) Closed Cup\",\"Melting Point: 74.8 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 118.17 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8726,'GLYCOL ETHER EE','101413','GCC','110-80-5','1','glycol-ether-ee','Clear colorless liquid with a pleasant ether odor',NULL,'It has the useful property of being able to dissolve chemically diverse compounds. It will dissolve oils, resins, grease, waxes, nitrocellulose, and lacquers. This is an ideal property as a multi-purpose cleaner, and, therefore, 2-ethoxyethanol is used in products, such as varnish removers and degreasing solutions.','Glycol Ether EE; 2-ethoxyethanol-ÿethylene glycol monoethyl ether-ÿethylene glycol ethyl ether-ÿEEÿ; Unicol EE','Store in a cool, dry environment, preferably in original containers, away from sources of ignitionÿ& oxidisingÿagents.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"415 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Solvents\"]','C4H10O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 43oC\\u00ff(110oF) Closed\\u00ffCup\",\"Melting Point: -70 \\u00f8C (-94 \\u00f8F)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 90.12 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8727,'GLYCOLIC ACID 57% TECH','101414','GCC','79-14-1, Mixture','1','glycolic-acid-57-tech','Clear colorless liquid with a mild burnt sugar odor',NULL,'Glycolic acid is used in the textile industry as a dyeing and tanning agent. It is also used in adhesives and plastics. Glycolic acid is often included into emulsion polymers, solvents and additives for ink and paint in order to improve flow properties and impart gloss. It is used in surface treatment products that increase the coefficient of friction on tile flooring.','Glycolic Acid 57% Tech; Ucare G-57; 2-Hydroxyacetic Acid; 2-Hydroxyethanoic Acid; GlyPure; NSC 166','Store in a cool place. Keep container tightly closed in a dry and well-ventilated place.','[\"75 kg. Poly Drum\",\"250 kg. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Dyes\",\"emulsifiers\",\"solvents\",\"acidulants\"]','C2H4O3','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 48580 SUB 3 CLASS 55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 129 \\u00f8C (264 \\u00f8F)\",\"Melting Point: 75 \\u00f8C (167 \\u00f8F)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 76.05 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8728,'GLYCOLIC ACID 70% COSMETIC GRADE','101415','GCC','79-14-1, Mixture','1','glycolic-acid-70-cosmetic-grade','Colorless, transparent liquid',NULL,'Glycolic Acid is used by the cosmetic industry to exfoliate the Stratum Corneum (the outer layer of skin), by peeling away dead cells a