; Instant Gum AA; Valspray A','Keep containers tightly closed. Store in a well-ventilated area.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 lb. HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 lb. Drum\",\"50 lb. Bag\",\"50 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"25 kg. Bag\",\"55 lb. Bag\",\"55 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"food & bev.\"]','[\"Gums\",\"sweetener\",\"thickeners\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:55','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8756,'GUM ARABIC SPRAY DRIED NF FCC','101444','GCC','2593228','1','gum-arabic-spray-dried-nf-fcc','White to tan powder','Is a natural gum made of hardened sap taken from two species of the acacia tree; Acacia senegal and Acacia seyal. It is used primarily in the food industry as a stabilizer. It\'s mixture of polysaccharides and glycoproteins gives it the properties of a glue and binder which is edible by humans. Acacia farnesiana is used in the perfume industry due to its strong fragrance.','Gum Arabic is used in sweeteners and as a food, beverage and drink additive, a liquid or drink thickener, in cake and pastry preparation, and in food flavorings. Gum Arabic is used to manufacture pharmaceutical capsules, to coat pills, and it is used to manufacture vitamins, lotions, mascara, cake makeup, and so on.','Gum Arabic Spray Dried NF FCC; Acacia; Unigum GA100; Acacia ampliceps gum; Arabic Cool SS; Instant Gum AA; Valspray A','Keep containers tightly closed. Store in a well-ventilated area. Keep away from moisture.','[\"55 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"270 lb. Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\",\"food & bev.\",\"pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Gums\",\"sweetener\",\"thickeners\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\"