ity, do not store in heat or direct sunlight.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"37 lb. Blue OH Pail\",\"400 lb. Steel Drum\",\"450 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emulsifiers\",\"surfactants\"]','(C2H4O)nC18H38O','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8903,'ISOSTEARETH-20','101652','GCC','52292-17-8','1','isosteareth-20','Light yellow paste',NULL,'Is a non-ionic surfactant and O/W emulsifier for advanced microemulsions.','Isosteareth-20; POE(20) Isostearyl Ether; Uneth-20; Agnique MMF; Aldol 66E20; Isostearyl alcohol-polyethylene glycol adduct','Keep containers closed until used. To maintain product quality, do not store in heat or direct sunlight.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"440 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emulsifiers\",\"surfactants\"]','(C2H4O)nC18H38O','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8904,'ISOSTEARIC ACID','101654','GCC','30399-84-9','1','isostearic-acid','Colorless to light yellow viscous liquid',NULL,'It serves as a smooth, dry feeling emollient able to assist the skin in replenishing its natural moisture. Also, Isostearic Acid when neutralized serves as an extremely effective and stable co-emulsifier used in the preparation of oil in water, low viscosity emulsion systems. When incorporated in a formulation in place of stearic acid, it reduces the fatty feel to a non-fatty feel. Isostearic Acid-s applications include skin creams, lotions, moisturizing creams, color cosmetics, sunscreen preparations, and shower gel formulations.','Isostearic Acid; Century 1105; Isooctadecanoic Acid; Radiacid 0908; Unistar ISA; Unimac 5680; Jaric I 18IG','Do not store at a temperature exceeding 80 øC. Store in a dry, cool, well-ventilated area. Store in the dark.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"38 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"397 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Fatty acids\",\"emollients & esters\",\"emulsifiers\"]','C18H36O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 192\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 10 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 284.48 g\\/mole\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8905,'ISOSTEARYL ALCOHOL','101656','GCC','27458-93-1','1','isostearyl-alcohol','Clear yellowish liquid',NULL,'It gives the skin a silky smooth feeling after product application.','Isostearyl Alcohol; Jeecol ISA; Jarcol I-18 CG; Unipro ISA; Aldo 66; Fine oxocol; Isooctadecan-1-ol','Keep in original container, tightly closed.','[\"250 ml. Glass Bottle\",\"35 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"375 lb. Steel Drum\",\"381 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"foam & viscosity boosters\",\"fatty alcohols\"]','C18H38O','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 102120 CLASS 60\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 124.9\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 270.49 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8906,'ISOSTEARYL ETHYLIMIDAZOLINIUM ETHOSULFATE','101658','GCC','None','1','isostearyl-ethylimidazolinium-ethosulfate','QC: DARK AMBER LIQUID',NULL,NULL,'SYN: MONAQUAT ISIES; ISOSTEARYL ETHYLIMIDONIUM ETHOSULFATE',NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8907,'ISOSTEARYL ISOSTEARATE','101659','GCC','41669-30-1','1','isostearyl-isostearate','Clear light yellow liquid with mild characteristic odor',NULL,'Isostearyl Isostearate is a fluid emollient for oils. It provides a rich feel and improves spreading on the skin. It is appropriate for use in lipsticks and as a binding agent for make-up powders. This product does not modify pigment coloration, and provides superfatting properties to compensate for the drying effect of powders.','Coster5088; Isostearyl isostearate; Pelemol II; Prisorine 2039; Prisorine ISIS 2039; Unimol ISS','Store in tightly closed containers. Store away from light and moisture.','[\"5 Gallon Blue TH Pail\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"binders\"]','C36H72O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: N\\/A\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 287.2 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 536.96 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8908,'ISOSTEARYL LINOLEATE','101660','GCC','127358-80-9','1','isostearyl-linoleate','Yellow oily liquid',NULL,'Isostearyl Linoleate has superior moisturization properties as well as excellent pigment dispersing properties and therefore may be used in various types or make-up, lip gloss or lipstick, mascara formulations. It can replace mineral oil or plant oils in creams or lotions that tend to be greasy. Isosteary Linoleate can also be used in sunscreen and hair conditioning products.','Isostearyl Linoleate; Protachem ISL; 9,12-Octadecadienoicacid (Z,Z)-, isooctadecyl ester; Isostearyl linoleate; Unimol ISL','Store in a dry, dark, well-ventilated area.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"20 lb. Pail\",\"40 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"moisturizer\"]','C36H68O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: >230 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: -5oC\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 532.92 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8909,'ISOSTEARYL NEOPENTANOATE','101661','GCC','58958-60-4','1','isostearyl-neopentanoate','Clear liquid with mild odor',NULL,'Is a low cloud point emollient for bath oils, creams and lotions that imparts freeze-thaw stability. I It is also a binder for pigment systems in make-up preparations.','Ceraphyl 375; Isostearyl Neopentanoate; Unaphyl 375; Crodamol ISNP; Dermol 185; Isostearyl pivalate','Keep container closed when not in use. Store in dry, cool area.','[\"400 lb. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"binders\"]','C23H46O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 196\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 354.69 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8910,'ISOSTEARYL PALMITATE','101663','GCC','72576-80-8','1','isostearyl-palmitate','Clear oily liquid',NULL,'Cosmetic liquid emollient offering excellent pour and mold-release properties while imparting remarkable spreadability. It functions as a co-solubilizer for silicones and waxes in sunscreens. Even at low concentrations, it imparts a light, silky emolliency and can eliminate the greasy feel of mineral oils and heavy esters.','Isostearyl Palmitate; Dermol ISP; Hexadecanoic acid, isooctadecyl ester; Unimol ISP; Isooctadecyl hexadecanoate','Store in a cool, dry, well ventilated place and out of direct sunlight. Store away from sources of heat or ignition. Protect from freezing. Store away from incompatible materials.','[\"100 ml. Glass Bottle\",\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"40 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"390 lb. Steel Drum\",\"400 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\"]','C34H68O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classifi