10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8913,'JOJOBA OIL CLEAR DEODORIZED REFINED','101666','GCC','61789-91-1','1','jojoba-oil-clear-deodorized-refined','Clear colorless liquid',NULL,'Jojoba oil is found in many cosmetic and pharmaceutical products and is a favorite among massage therapists. It is has exceptional glide as if one is being massaged by pure silk. Because of its amazing capacity to be absorbed by our skin, Jojoba oil does not stain massage sheets, nor does it leave a residue on massage clients.','Jojoba Oil Deod Ref [CLEAR]; Jojoba Oil Ultra Refined Deodorized Colorless; Simmondsia Chinensis; Unoil JO-10','Keep stored in a cool, dry area. Do not store in heat or direct sunlight, and keep from freezing.','[\"100 ml. Glass Bottle\",\"250 ml. Glass Bottle\",\"35 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"25 kg. Pail\",\"180 kg. Steel Drum\",\"180 kg. Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\",\"pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"moisturizer\",\"absorption bases\",\"essential oils\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Natural\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 145150 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: > 290\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 66-73\\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8914,'JOJOBA OIL GOLDEN ORGANIC','101667','GCC','61789-91-1','1','jojoba-oil-golden-organic','Clear golden yellow oily liquid',NULL,'Jojoba oil is found in many cosmetic and pharmaceutical products and is a favorite among massage therapists. It is has exceptional glide as if one is being massaged by pure silk. Because of its amazing capacity to be absorbed by our skin, Jojoba oil does not stain massage sheets, nor does it leave a residue on massage clients.','Jojoba Oil Golden Organic; Unoil JO-20G; Simmondsia Chinensis','Keep stored in a cool, dry area. Do not store in heat or direct sunlight, and keep from freezing.','[\"100 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"250 ml. HDPE Bott