ottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"cosmetics\"]','[\"Active pharmaceutical ingredient\"]','C26H28Cl2N4O4','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 409.4 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 145-146 \\u00f8C\",\"API: YES\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 531.4 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8927,'KOJIC ACID','101680','GCC','501-30-4','1','kojic-acid','Tan crystalline powder',NULL,'It is applied as a skin lightening agent due to its potential to inhibit the enzyme tyrosinase. Tyrosinase is necessary for the synthesis of melanin, which offers skin its coloring. Kojic Acid also has antibacterial, antifungal and antioxidant attributes. It can protect against fruits from turning brown and is also applied to preserve the pink and red shade of seafood.','Kojic Acid; Unojic KA; 5-Hydroxy-2-hydroxymethyl-4H-pyran-4-one','Store in a cool, dry place. Store in a tightly closed container.','[\"25 Gram Poly Bag\",\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"1 kg. Bottle\",\"5 kg. Bag\",\"5 kg. HDPE OH Pail\",\"10 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\",\"food & bev.\"]','[\"Preservatives\\/natural\"]','C6H6O4','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 179.9 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 152-155 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 142.11 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8928,'KOKUM BUTTER','101681','GCC','68956-68-3','1','kokum-butter','White solid fat',NULL,'Kokum butter is rich in essential fatty acids, which aid in cell oxygenation and make nutrients more readily available for use by skin tissues. Kokum butter also contains antioxidant vitamin E. Kokum butter is a non-comedogenic (non pore-clogging) material that aids quick absorption and adds a premium texture to your cream emulsions. Kokum butter helps regenerate tired and worn skin cells and supports skin elasticity and general flexibility of the skin wall. It has been used traditionally in India to soften skin and restore elasticity and as a balm for dry, cracked, rough, and calloused skin.','Kokum Butter; Unibut KK; Gold of Pleasure Oil; Goa butter; Kokum oil; Mangosteen oil','Store in closed containers below 25§C, in a well ventillated area.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 kg. Box\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Botanicals\",\"fatty acids\",\"vitamins\",\"vegetable oils\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: >250\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8929,'KUKUI NUT OIL','101682','GCC','8015-80-3','1','kukui-nut-oil','Pale yellow to amber oily liquid',NULL,'Kukui nut oil is reported to have excellent penetration properties, to aid in soothing and moisturizing the skin, and relieve chapped skin and irritations. It does not leave the skin with a greasy afterfeel. It is a sunscreen solubilizer that reduces the greasy feel often associated with sun products. It is also an excellent treatment for psoriasis and eczema, and is also beneficial for acne and other common skin disorders.','Kukui Nut Oil; Unoil KN; Candle nutoil; Kukui nut oil; Oils, Candlenut','Store in closed containers below 30oC in a well-ventilated area. Store away from oxidizing agents, excessive heat, sources of ignition such as sparks, flames, and sunlight.','[\"50 ml. Bottle\",\"250 ml. Glass Bottle\",\"38 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"39lb. HDPE OH Pail\",\"420 lb. Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Botanicals\",\"essential oils\",\"fatty acids\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 50-54 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8930,'LACTAMIDE MEA','101683','GCC','5422-34-4','1','lactamide-mea','Brownish viscous liquid',NULL,'Is a surfactant that can also act as a thickener, foam booster, and stabilizer. Is used in cosmetic applications.','Lactamide MEA; Unamide MEA; 2-hydroxy-n-(2-hydroxyethyl)-propanamid; Mackamide LME; Monoethanolamine lactic acid amide','Keep away from heat and sources of ignition. When not in use, tightly seal the container and store in a dry, cool place.','[\"450 lb. Steel Drum\",\"500 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Surfactants\",\"thickeners\",\"foam & viscosity boosters\",\"stabilizer\"]','C5H11NO3','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 183.8\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 133.15 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(8931,'LACTIC ACID 50% NATL FCC','101684','GCC','598-82-3','1','lactic-acid-50-natl-fcc','Colorless to yellow syrupy liquid',NULL,'In food, apart from its nutritional function for normal growth, it improves flavor and taste, improves quality of food and beverage products such as confectionery, cake, milk powder, yogurt etc. as firming agent, buffering agent and flour regulator. It increases effectiveness of antioxidants, prevents decolorization of fruits and vegetables.','Lactic Acid 50% NATL FCC; Purac FCC 50; Unilac LA50; Tisulac; Espiritin; HiPure 90; l-lacticaci; Lactic L-Milchsàure','Store in a tightly closed container. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated 