\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 150.22 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9019,'L-CYSTEINE BASE','101807','GCC','52-90-4','1','l-cysteine-base','White crystalline powder',NULL,'In pharmaceutical industry, Cysteine is used in the treatment of radioactive drugs poison, heavy metal poison, toxic hepatitis, serum sickness, and can prevent liver degeneration. The cosmetic grade is used in skin whitening products, dissolving cutin, and anti-aging.','L-Cysteine Base; Unicist LCB; Cys; 3-mercapto-l-alanin; FEMA 3263; (R)-2-Amino-3-mercaptopropanoic acid','Store in cool & dry place. Keep away from strong light and heat.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 lb. HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 kg. HDPE OH Pail\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"cosmetics\"]','[\"Amino acids\",\"vitamins\"]','C3H7NO2S','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 131.5\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 220 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 121.16 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9020,'L-CYSTEINE HCL ANHYDROUS','101808','GCC','56-89-3','1','l-cysteine-hcl-anhydrous','White powder or crystals',NULL,'Used in biochemical research and used as a preparation of biological medium. Used in biochemical and nutritional research, medicine has the body to promote the cell oxidation and reduction function, increase white blood cell and prevent pathogens such as development role. Mainly used for all kinds of hair loss syndrome. Also used for dysentery, typhoid, influenza and acute infectious disease, asthma, neuralgia, eczema, and various poisoning disease, etc., and maintain the function of protein configuration. They are also used as food additive agent.','L-Cysteine HCL Anhydrous; Nephrin;h-(cys); Unicist LCA; Dicysteine; ;1-Cystine','Store in a cool, dry place. Store in a tightly closed container.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"20 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"cosmetics\",\"food & bev.\"]','[\"Amino acids\"]','C6H12N2O4S2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 237 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: >240 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 240.3 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9021,'L-CYSTEINE HCL MONOHYDRATE FCC','101809','GCC','1880366','1','l-cysteine-hcl-monohydrate-fcc','White crystalline powder',NULL,'L-Cysteine is a non-essential amino acid that can be synthesized by the human body under normal physiological conditions if a sufficient quantity of methionine is available. L-Cysteine is commonly use d as a precursor in the food and pharmaceutical industries. L-Cysteine is used as a processing aid for baking, as an additive in cigarettes, as well as in the preparation of meat flavors.','L-Cystiene HCL Monohydrate FCC; Unicist LCM40; alpha-amino-beta-mercapto-propionic acid hydrochloride monohydrate; H-CYS-OH HCL H2O','Store in a tightly closed container. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area away from incompatible substances. Keep away from metals. Keep refrigerated.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"10 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"food & bev.\"]','[\"Amino acids\"]','C3H10ClNO3S','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 131.5 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 175\\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 175.63 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9022,'L-CYSTEINE HCL MONOHYDRATE FCC KOSHER','101810','GCC','1880366','1','l-cysteine-hcl-monohydrate-fcc-kosher','White crystalline powder',NULL,'L-Cysteine is a non-essential amino acid that can be synthesized by the human body under normal physiological conditions if a sufficient quantity of methionine is available. L-Cysteine is commonly use d as a precursor in the food and pharmaceutical industries. L-Cysteine is used as a processing aid for baking, as an additive in cigarettes, as well as in the preparation of meat flavors.','L-Cystiene HCL Monohydrate FCC Kosher; Unicist LCM; alpha-amino-beta-mercapto-propionic acid hydrochloride monohydrate; H-CYS-OH HCL H2O','Store in a tightly closed container. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area away from incompatible substances. Keep away from metals. Keep refrigerated.','[\"100 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"food & bev.\"]','[\"Amino acids\"]','C3H10ClNO3S','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 131.5 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 175\\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 175.63 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9023,'L-CYSTINE FREE BASE','101811','GCC','56-89-3','1','l-cystine-free-base','White crystalline powder',NULL,'L- Cystine helps strengthen the immune system, reduce damage from free-radicals, repair RNA-DNA in the cells and assimilation of vitamin B6. L-Cystine is closely related to the amino acid, L-Cysteine. L-Cystine aids in preventing the side effects of chemotherapy and radiation. It increases L-Glutathione levels in the lungs, liver, kidney and bone marrow. L-Cystine also has an anti-aging effect on the body which can reduce the accumulation of age spots.','L-Cystine Free Base; Unitine LCB; Nephrin; h-(cys);l-cystin; Dicysteine; Cystin','Store in cool & dry place. Keep away from strong light and heat.','[\"50 Gram Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 lb. HDPE OH Pail\",\"10 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"10 lb. HDPE OH Pail\",\"20 kg. Box\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"cosmetics\"]','[\"Amino acids\"]','C6H12N2O4S2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 237 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: >240 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 240.3 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9024,'L-DMAE BITARTRATE POWDER','101812','GCC','5988-51-2','1','l-dmae-bitartrate-powder','White crystalline powder','It is also used as a food additive and food nutritive fortifier.','DMAE boosts brain function by causing the body to produce more acetylcholine, a neurotransmitter that sends messages and commands concerning emotions and behavior throughout the brain. DMAE supplements are widely available in liquid, capsule, tablet, and cream forms. DMAE creams have demonstrated an ability to help tighten skin and fade age spots, although it is not certain how it achieves these results.','L-DMAE Bitartrate Powder; Atrol; 2-(dimethylamino)-ethanoltartrate; Dimethaen; ethanol,2-(dimethylamino)-,(r-(r*,r))-2,3-dihydroxybutanedioate(1:1)(salt','Store in a cool, dry place. Store in a tightly closed container.','[\"10 Gram Bag\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"cosmetics\",\"food & bev.\"]','[\"Amino acids\",\"Vitamins\",\"nutritional supplements\"]','C4H11NOC4H6O6','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 209.4 \\u00a7C\",\"Melting Point: 109-113 \\u00a7C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 239.22 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9025,'LEAD ACETATE TECH FLAKES','101813','GCC','301-04-2','1','lead-acetate-tech-flakes','White flakes',NULL,'Used in men\'s hair coloring products. Lead(II) acetate paper is used to detect the poisonous gas hydrogen sulfi