on of the linoleic acid with oxygen in air, which leads to crosslinking and formation of a stable film.','Linolenic Acid 75%; Unilenic A75; 9-cis,12-cis-Linoleic acid; cis-9,cis-12-Octadecadienoic acid; Telfairic acid','No special instructions.','[\"175 kg. Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\",\"cosmetics\"]','[\"Fatty acids\",\"oils\",\"surfactant\"]','C18H32O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: N\\/A\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 112 \\u00f8C (234 \\u00f8F)\",\"Melting Point: -5 \\u00f8C (23 \\u00f8F)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 280.45 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9058,'LINSEED OIL','101849','GCC','8001-26-1','1','linseed-oil','Yellow or golden yellow liquid',NULL,'Its botanical properties are listed as emollient, anti-inflammatory, and healing. It is derived from the flas plant seed.','Linseed Oil; Unoil LIN20; Acid Refined Linseed Oil; Flaxseed Oil; Linseed oil fatty acids ;Purolin','Store at room temperature in tightly sealed containers.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"18 kg. Pail\",\"410 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Botanicals\",\"emollient & esters\",\"fatty acids\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 222 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: -19oC\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9059,'LINSEED OIL REFINED','101850','GCC','8001-26-1','1','linseed-oil-refined','Pale yellow oily liquid',NULL,'Linseed oil refined is a versatile drying oil used in paints and coatings for its film forming and fast drying capabilities. It can also be used as a binder and for surface coatings in hardboard manufacturing. Dryers and other compounds are often added to impart specific functionality.','Linseed Oil Refined; Unoil LIN40; Acid Refined Linseed Oil; Flaxseed Oil; Linseed oil fatty acids ;Purolin','Store at room temperature in tightly sealed containers.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"190 kg. Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Binders\",\"coating and sealants chemicals\",\"fatty acids\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 48580 SUB 3 CLASS 55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 222 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: -19oC\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9060,'LIQUID ABSORPTION BASE','101851','GCC','MIXTURE','1','liquid-absorption-base',NULL,NULL,NULL,'SYN: EMERY 1732',NULL,'[null]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9061,'L-ISOLEUCINE USP','101852','GCC','73-32-5','1','l-isoleucine-usp','White crystalline powder',NULL,'Isoleucine is widely recognized as an amino acid able to increase endurance and to help heal muscle tissue. It is particularly recommended to professional athletes and body builders, as the primary function of Isoleucine in the body is to boost up the energy levels and to assist the body in recovering from strenuous physical activity.','L-Isoleucine USP; Unocine IL; ILE; (2S,3S)-2-Amino-3-methylpentansàure; H-ILE-OH; (2S)-2-Amino-3-Methylpentanoic Acid','Keep in a tightly closed container, stored in a cool, dry, ventilated area. Protect from physical damage.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"5 kg. HDPE OH Pail\",\"25 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Amino acids\"]','C6H13NO2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 168-170\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 288 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 131.17 g\\/mol\"]','2025-