,NULL,'Leucine is considered a vital amino acid for the protein synthesis and various metabolic functions - in other words, it is an essential amino acid, which helps in regulating the blood-sugar levels, promotes the growth and the recovery of muscle and bone tissues, as well as the production of the growth hormone. This amino acid is also known for preventing the breakdown of muscle proteins caused by injury or stress. In addition, Leucine may be beneficial for people suffering from phenylketonuria.','L-Leucine; Unisine L40; H-L-LEU-OH; Rarechem AB PP 3754; 2-Amino-4-methylpentanoic acid; (s)-2-amino-4-methylvalericacid','Keep in a tightly closed container, stored in a cool, dry, ventilated area. Protect from moisture and light.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 kg. Box\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Amino acid\",\"vitamins\"]','C6H13NO2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 145-148\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: >300 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 131.17 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9069,'L-LEUCINE USP','101862','GCC','61-90-5','1','l-leucine-usp','White crystalline powder',NULL,'Leucine is considered a vital amino acid for the protein synthesis and various metabolic functions - in other words, it is an essential amino acid, which helps in regulating the blood-sugar levels, promotes the growth and the recovery of muscle and bone tissues, as well as the production of the growth hormone. This amino acid is also known for preventing the breakdown of muscle proteins caused by injury or stress. In addition, Leucine may be beneficial for people suffering from phenylketonuria.','L-Leucine USP; Unisine LE; H-L-LEU-OH; Rarechem AB PP 3754; 2-Amino-4-methylpentanoic acid; (s)-2-amino-4-methylvalericacid','Keep in a tightly closed container, stored in a cool, dry, ventilated area. Protect from moisture and light.','[\"30 Gram Bag\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 kg. HDPE OH Pail\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Amino acid\",\"vitamins\"]','C6H13NO2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 145-148\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: >300 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 131.17 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9070,'L-LYSINE HCL USP GRANULAR K','101863','GCC','657-27-2','1','l-lysine-hcl-usp-granular-k','White crystalline powder',NULL,'Lysine can enhance animal appetite, improve body\'s resistance to disease and promote growth. Proper adding of lysine in animal grain feed can not only accelerate the growth of livestock and poultry, shorten herds period, but also greatly increase the proportion of lean meat. Besides, pork or chicken taste better by adding lysine into feed for pigs and chicken.','L-Lysine HCL USP Granular K; Unsine LH20; L-Gen; NSC 9253; Darvyl; Lysion','Store at room temperature. Keep container tightly closed and dry.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 lb. HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 kg. HDPE OH Pail\",\"25 kg. Bag\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"50 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"food & bev.\"]','[\"Amino acid\"]','C6H15ClN2O2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 142.2 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 263 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 182.65 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9071,'L-LYSINE HCL USP POWDER 100 MESH KOSHER','101864','GCC','657-27-2','1','l-lysine-hcl-usp-powder-100-mesh-kosher','White crystalline powder',NULL,'Lysine can enhance animal appetite, improve body\'s resistance to disea