ER','101866','GCC','2216-51-5','1','l-menthol-usp-large-crystal-kosher','Colorless, needle-like or prism-like crystals with a minty odor',NULL,'Menthol crystals are cooling, refreshing, and have a pleasantly strong minty aroma. They are often used in cosmetics, salves, balms, medicated creams, throat lozenges, toothpaste, mouthwash, gum, foot sprays, pain relief or cooling body products, shampoos, conditioners, liniments, shaving creams, oral or throat sprays, compresses, medicated oils, and cooling gels. Menthol crystals are excellent for use in these products to help relieve muscular aches and pains, coughing, congestion, the flu, and upper respiratory problems. Since Menthol crystals are so concentrated, only a very small amount is needed within products.','L-Menthol USP/NF Crystal; TN: Unichem Ment; Unichem MEN-10; (1R,2S,5R)-2-Isopropyl-5- methylcyclohexan-1-ol; L-Mentholum; Levomenthol','Keep container tightly closed in a cool, dry and well-ventilated place.','[\"50 Gram Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 lb. HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 kg. HDPE OH Pail\",\"25 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"25 kg. Drum [AR]\",\"25 kg. Drum [C]\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"25 kg. Drum [S]\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\",\"pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Flavors\"]','C10H20O','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 200 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: 41-44 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 156.27 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9074,'L-MENTHOL USP LARGE CRYSTALS','101867','GCC','2216-51-5','1','l-menthol-usp-large-crystals','Colorless, needle-like or prism-like crystals with a minty odor',NULL,'Menthol crystals are cooling, refreshing, and have a pleasantly strong minty aroma. They are often used in cosmetics, salves, balms, medicated creams, throat lozenges, toothpaste, mouthwash, gum, foot sprays, pain relief or cooling body products, shampoos, conditioners, liniments, shaving creams, oral or throat sprays, compresses, medicated oils, and cooling gels. Menthol crystals are excellent for use in these products to help relieve muscular aches and pains, coughing, congestion, the flu, and upper respiratory problems. Since Menthol crystals are so concentrated, only a very small amount is needed within products.','L-Menthol USP Large Crystals; Unichem MEN-20; (1R,2S,5R)-2-Isopropyl-5- methylcyclohexan-1-ol; L-Mentholum; Levomenthol','Keep container tightly closed in a cool, dry and well-ventilated place.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\",\"pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Flavors\"]','C10H20O','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 200 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: 41-44 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 156.27 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9075,'L-METHIONINE USP','101868','GCC','63-68-3','1','l-methionine-usp','White crystalline powder or crystals','Methionine, organic compound, one of the 20 amino acids commonly found in animal proteins. Methionine is one of the several essential amino acids needed in the diet; the human body cannot synthesize it from simpler metabolites. Methionine supplies sulfur and other compounds required by the body for normal metabolism and growth. It is an important source of dietary sulfur. Methionine also belongs to a group of compounds called lipotropics; others in this group include choline, inositol, and betaine. Methionine is one of only two amino acids encoded by just one codon (AUG) in the standard genetic code (tryptophan, encoded by UGG, is the other). L-methionine is a sulfur-containing amino acid that is minimally soluble in water. Its sulfur is non reactive.','Methionine is a sulfur-containing proteinogenic amino acid, acting as an intermediate in the biosynthesis of different phospholipids. It is important in single-carbon metabolism and helps the detoxification in the liver. Meanwhile, improper conversion of Methionine can lead to atherosclerosis.','L-Methionine USP; Unine 100; Acimethin; Cymethion; Liquimeth; L-Lobamine; Unichem LMT-20','Store in light-resistant containers. Keep container tightly closed in a dry and well-ventilated place. Store at room temperature in the original container. Store away from incompatible materials.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Amino acid\"]','C5H11NO2S','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 139.4\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 284 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 149.21 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9076,'L-ORNITHINE MONOHYDROCHLORIDE','101869','GCC','3184-13-2','1','l-ornithine-monohydrochloride','White crystalline powder',NULL,'Is a central part of the urea cycle, which allows for the disposal of excess nitrogen.','L-Ornithine Monohydrochloride; L-2,5-Diamopentanoic Acid Monohydrochloride; (S)-(+)-2,5-Diaminopentanoic acid hydrochloride; L-2,5-Diaminovaleric acid; Unichem LOR50','Keep container tightly closed in a dry and well-ventilated place.','[\"50 Gram Bottle\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Nutraceutical supplements\",\"amino acid\"]','C5H12N2O2HCl','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 5 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 245 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 168.62 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9077,'L-PHENYLALANINE','101870','GCC','63-91-2','1','l-phenylalanine','White crystalline 