mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9222,'MICROCRYSTALLINE WAX AMBER','102017','GCC','63231-60-7','1','microcrystalline-wax-amber','Off-white to amber colored chunks','Wax with ability to bind oils & solvents (prevent sweating of lipsticks), crystals insure high tensile strength & consistency (more malleable than paraffin), insures color uniformity in color cosmetics, compatible with all kinds of oils & waxes.','Used in all kinds of stick cosmetics such as lipsticks, lip balm, concealers, and deodorants. It is also used in emulsions like creams and lotions.','Microcrystalline Wax Amber; Bard’s TackyWax; Be Square 175Amber; Microflex M 4; Paraffinwaxes and Hydrocarbon waxes, microcryst','Keep containers tightly closed. Store in a cool, dry well-ventilated area away from heat and all sources of ignition.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"55 lb. Box\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Binders\",\"emulsifier\",\"waxes\",\"petrolatums\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: > 400\\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: 170-180\\u00f8F\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9223,'MICROPURE EG','102018','GCC','872-50-4','1','micropure-eg','Colorless to light yellow liquid with an amine odor',NULL,'NMP is used to recover certain hydrocarbons generated in the processing petrochemicals, such as the recovery of 1,3-butadiene and acetylene. It is used to absorb hydrogen sulfide from sour gas and hydrodesulfurization facilities. Due to its good solvency properties NMP is used to dissolve a wide range of polymers. It also used as a solvent for surface treatment of textiles, resins, and metal coated plastics or as a paint stripper.','Micropure EG,; N-Methyl-2-Pyrrolidone; Pharmasolve; Pyrol M; 1-Methyl-5-pyrrolidinone; N-Methyl-a-pyrrolidone','Keep in a tightly closed container. Store in a cool, dry, ventilated area away from sources of heat or ignition. Protect against physical damage.','[\"250 ml. Glass Bottle\",\"460 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Solvents\",\"petrolatums\"]','C5H9NO','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 91 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: -24 \\u00f8C (-11 \\u00f8F)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 99.13 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9224,'MILK PEPTIDE COMPLEX CLR','102019','GCC','Mixture','1','milk-peptide-complex-clr','Clear liquid',NULL,'MPC contains the network of natural signal molecules of milk in their activated form. These are protected by a physiological environment of milk components such as lactoglobulin, lactalbumin, lactoferrin, lactose and other carriers. It is recommended for use in emulsified and gel-type skin regenerating preparations designed for mature skin and for prevention of accelerated skin aging caused by environmental influences.','Milk Peptide Complex Clr; Unitide MPC; Whey Protein','Store in tightly sealed containers, protected from light.','[\"1 kg. Bottle\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Proteins\",\"lactate & lactic acid\",\"emulsifier\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NON REGULATED CHEMICALS NOI CLASS 55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9225,'MILK PROTEIN 80% CMP-GP KOSHER','102020','GCC','Unassigned','1','milk-protein-80-cmp-gp-kosher','102020',NULL,'It gives a smooth feel to the skin. Milk protein is primarily casein that is well absorbed by the skin, and gives it a gloss and fine touch by forming a soft film.','Milk Protein 80% CMP-G