 kg. Bag\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Proteins\",\"lactate & lactic acid\",\"emulsifier\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9228,'MILK THISTLE 80%','102023','GCC','None','1','milk-thistle-80','Light yellow powder with characteristic odor',NULL,'Credited with wound-healing. It is used in toners and aftershave preparations. Milk thistle is used most often for liver disorders, including liver damage caused by chemicals, Amanita phalloides mushroom poisoning, jaundice, chronic inflammatory liver disease, cirrhosis of the liver, and chronic hepatitis. Milk thistle is also used for loss of appetite, heartburn (dyspepsia), and gallbladder complaints.','Milk Thistle 80%; Artichaut Sauvage; Carduus marianus; Blessed Milk Thistle; Silybin; Silybum','Store in tightly closed containers in a cool, dry area.','[null]','[null]','[\"25 Gram Poly Bag\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9229,'MINERAL JELLY #15','102024','GCC','2231335','1','mineral-jelly-15','Off-white semi-solid',NULL,'Most uses for petroleum jelly exploit its lubricating, coating and moisturizing potentials. Most petroleum jelly today is used as an ingredient in skin lotions and cosmetics, providing various types of skin care and protection by minimizing friction or reducing moisture loss, or by functioning as a grooming aid. Petroleum jelly is used to gently clean a variety of surfaces, ranging from makeup removal from faces to tar stain removal from leather.','Mineral Jelly #15; Petrolatum; White petroleum jelly; Vaseline; Paraffin jelly; Mineral fat; Ultima white','Store in a cool, dry area. Keep away from heat/sparks/open flames/hot surfaces.','[\"375 lb. Drum\",\"386 lb. Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Petrolatums\",\"minerals\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 198 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 70-80 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9230,'MINERAL OIL #70 (CARNATION)','102025','GCC','8042-47-5','1','mineral-oil-70-carnation','Colorless transparent oily liquid',NULL,'Is an emollient cleanser and demulsifier of dirt trapped in pores. Mineral oil is excellent for use in cleaners. In leave-on cosmtics, its comedogenicity or lack thereof appears related to the level of raw material refinement; therefore, some suppliers state that their product is noncomedogenic. When used in leave-on preparations, mineral oil\'s occlusive capability is considered to help improve the epidermal barrier function.','Mineral Oil #70 (Carnation); Liquid Petrolatum; Paraffin Oil, White; White Mineral Oil','Keep containers closed when not in use. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"5 Gallon Blue TH Pail\",\"35 lb. HDPE OH Pail\",\"55 Gallon Steel Drum\",\"388 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Mineral oils\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 1\\/2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 365oF (185oC)\",\"Melting Point: <15oF (-9oC)\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9231,'MINERAL OIL 90 VIS [MARCOL 90]','102026','GCC','8012-95-1','1','mineral-oil-90-vis-marcol-90