ts\",\"emulsifiers\",\"emollient & esters\"]','C15H24O(C2H4O)n','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NON REGULATED CHEMICALS NOI CLASS 55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 535 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: 44-46 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9318,'NONOXYNOL 9','102120','GCC','26571-11-9','1','nonoxynol-9','Clear slightly viscous liquid',NULL,'Nonoxynol-9 is sometimes included in shaving creams for its properties as a nonionic surfactant; it helps break down skin oils that normally protect hair from moisture, so that they become wet and, hence, softer and easier to shave. As a spermicide, it attacks the acrosomal membranes of the sperm, causing the sperm to be immobilized. Nonoxynol-9 is the active ingredient in most spermicidal creams, jellies, foams, gel, film, and suppositories. Many models of condoms are lubricated with solutions containing nonoxynol-9.','Nonoxynol 9; T/N: Igepal CO-630; T/N: Tergitol NP-9-Surfactant; Nonoxynol-9 ( p-Nonylphenyl, Ethoxylated); alpha-(p-Nonylphenyl)-w-hydroxynona(oxyethylene)','Keep container tightly closed. Store in dry, cool place, and protect from moisture.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"40 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"470 lb. Steel Drum\",\"480 lb. Poly Drum\",\"480 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Surfactants\"]','C33H60O10','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 3 months from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 197\\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 6\\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 616.82 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9319,'NONYLPHENOXYPOLY (ETHYLENEOXY) ETHANOL','102122','GCC','9016-45-9','1','nonylphenoxypoly-ethyleneoxy-ethanol','CLEAR/HAZY LIQUID',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'[null]','[\"Soaps\"]','[null]',NULL,'[null]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9320,'N-PROPANOL','102123','GCC','71-23-8','1','n-propanol','Clear colorless liquid with a characteristic odor',NULL,'It is formed naturally in small amounts during many fermentation processes and used as a solvent in the pharmaceutical industry mainly for resins and cellulose esters. 1-propanol has high octane numbers and it is suitable to engine fuel usage. However, production of propanol has been too expensive to be a common fuel.','N-Propanol; 1-Propanol; Alcohol C3; 1-Hydroxypropane; Albacol; 1-Propyl alcohol','Keep container tightly closed in a dry and well-ventilated place. Containers which are opened must be carefully resealed and kept upright to prevent leakage.','[\"370 lb. Steel Drum\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"Industrial\"]','[\"Solvents\"]','C3H8O','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 48580 SUB 3 CLASS 55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 59 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: -127 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 60.10 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9321,'NUTMEG EAST INDIAN OIL','102124','GCC','8008-45-5','1','nutmeg-east-indian-oil','Colorless to light yellow oil',NULL,'The oil is used by the perfume and pharmaceutical industries. Nutmeg oil is also used as a natural food flavoring in baked goods, and in soda syrups, and sweets. It is often used as a replacement for ground nutmeg as it leaves no particles in the food. In the pharmaceutical industry the oil is used in tooth paste and as a major ingredient in several different brands of cough syrups.','Nutmeg East Indian Oil; Myristica Oil; Nutmeg Powder; Myristicaceae; Nutmegshelloil','Store in tightly closed original container, in a cool, dry & ventilated area away from heat sources & protected from light. Keep air contact to a minimum.','[\"25 lb. Pail\",\"169 kg. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Essential oils\",\"flavors\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 110 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9322,'NYLON -12','102125','GCC','Proprietary','1','nylon-12','Odorless powder','Is a polyamida powder for use in color cosmetics (ex: lipsticks, foundations, skin care, and sun care). It combines soft touch with good absorption properties and improves ease of application and spreadability. It also provides an enhancement of skin feel and a reduced shine on skin.','Has a high oil absorption and mattyfing properties. It also has less tackiness results and leaves skin feeling pleasant.','Tegolon 12-20; Nylon-12; Polyamide p-12; Poly[imino(1-oxo-1,12-dodecanediyl)]; Poly Lauryl Lactam','Storage temperature should not exceed 30 øC.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Absorption bases\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9323,'OATMEAL EXTRACT','102126','GCC','Mixture','1','oatmeal-extract','Light to clear yellow liquid',NULL,'Is soothing for all types of skin and especially popular in baby skin care products, Oat Extract is also considered moisturizing and mildly anti-aging.','Oatmeal Extract; Avena sativa flowering top; Green oat extract; White oat','Store in a cool, dry location, in a sealed container in a well-ventilated area. Keep away from sunlight.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Moisturizer\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf l