botanicals\",\"flavors\",\"fatty acids\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 225 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: -6 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9375,'OLIVE OIL PURE NF','102198','GCC','8001-25-0','1','olive-oil-pure-nf','Yellow to amber colored liquid with bland fatty odor',NULL,'Used in the pharmaceutical industry in many ways including: treating cardiovascular conditions, antibacterial, dermatitis, nutritional supplements, and for rheumatoid arthritis.','Olive Oil NF Pure; Olea europaea, Olive Oil Pure; Olive Oil, Extra Virgin','Store in a cool, dark area. Keep away from sources of heat.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"38 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"38 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"58 Gallon Steel Drum\",\"420 lb. Steel Drum\",\"200 kg. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Vegetable oils\",\"fatty acids\",\"nutritional supplements\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 225 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: -6 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9376,'OLIVE OIL PURE NF KOSHER','102199','GCC','8001-25-0','1','olive-oil-pure-nf-kosher','Yellow to amber colored liquid with bland fatty odor',NULL,'Used in the pharmaceutical industry in many ways including: treating cardiovascular conditions, antibacterial, dermatitis, nutritional supplements, and for rheumatoid arthritis.','Olive Oil Pure NF Kosher; T/N: Edible Olive Oil NF ‘OU’; Olea europaea, Olive Oil Extra Vigrin','Store in a cool, dark area. Keep away from sources of heat.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"38 lb. Blue TH Pail\",\"200 kg. Steel Drum\",\"420 l