ULL,NULL,'2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9544,'PEG 90 NF [ UNIPEG 4000X ]','102387','GCC','25322-68-3','1','peg-90-nf-unipeg-4000x','White crystalline granules',NULL,'Is widely used as excipients in a variety of pharmaceutical formulations, such as oral tablets and caplets, solutions and syrups, topical, rectal and vaginal preparations, ophtalmic, dental and parenteral systems. They function as solubilizer, dispersing agent, plasticizer, lubricant, emulsion stabilizer and as viscosity and consistency builder.','PEG 90 NF [Unipeg 4000X]; PEG-90 USP [Unipeg 4000X]; T/N: Polyglykol PEG 4000S; Canapeg 4000 USP NF','Store in original container. Use product promptly after opening. Avoid prolonged exposure to heat and air','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"44 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"44 lb. Bag\",\"50 lb. Bag\",\"25 kg. Bag\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Excipients\",\"stabilizer\",\"emulsifier\",\"plasticizer\",\"foam & viscosity booster\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 220\\u00f8 C (Closed Cup) 270\\u00f8 C (Open Cup)\",\"Melting Point: 57 - 59 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9545,'PEG E1000 NF P','102388','GCC','25322-68-3','1','peg-e1000-nf-p','White flakes',NULL,'This polymer is highly water soluble and acts as a solvent, plasticizer, surfactant in ointments and suppositories and as a lubricant for capsules and tablets.','PEG E1000 NF P; Unipeg 1000; Pluracol E1000; PEG E1000 USP','Store in tightly sealed container away from sources of heat.','[\"500 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Excipients\",\"surfactant\",\"solvent\",\"plasticizer\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 1\\/2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NON REGULATED CHEMICALS NOI CLASS 55\",