. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Chemicals general\"]','C9H14ClNO2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 163.4 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 143-145 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 203.67 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9598,'PHENYLETHYL ALCOHOL','102447','GCC','60-12-8','1','phenylethyl-alcohol','Clear colorless viscous liquid',NULL,'Is a common ingredient in flavors, particularly when the taste of rose is desired. Phenethyl alcohol is found in extract of rose, carnation, hyacinth, Aleppo pine, orange blossom, ylang-ylang, geranium, neroli, and champaca. It is also used as a preservative in soaps due to its stability in basic conditions. It is of interest due to its antimicrobial properties.','Phenyl Ethyl Alcohol FCC; Phenyl Ethyl Alcohol Frag. Grade; beta-Hydroxyethylbenzene; 2-Phenethyl Alcohol; Benzyl Carbinol; 2-Phenethanol; 1-Phenyl-2-ethanol','Store in a cool, dry place, with container tightly sealed.','[null]','[\"Food & bev.\",\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Flavors\",\"essential oils\",\"preservatives\\/antimicrobials\"]','C8H10O','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: UN 2810, TOXIC LIQUIDS, ORGANIC, N. O. S., ( PHENYLETHYL ALCOHOL ), 6.1, III, NA ERG# 153\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 216 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: -27 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 122.16 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9599,'PHENYL ETHYL ALCOHOL FCC','102448','GCC','60-12-8','1','phenyl-ethyl-alcohol-fcc','Clear colorless viscous liquid',NULL,'Is a common ingredient in flavors, particularly when the taste of rose is desired.','Phenyl Ethyl Alcohol FCC; beta-Hydroxyethylbenzene; 2-Phenethyl Alcohol; Benzyl Carbinol; 2-Phenethanol; 1-Phenyl-2-ethanol','Store in a cool, dry