y viscous liquid',NULL,'Polycare- 133 is an innovative highly charged cationic homopolymer which provides good conditioning and hold without film build up. Due to its unique chemistry and properties this product can be utilized in a broad spectrum of hair care applications such as styling gels, sprays, conditioners and mousses. Polycare- 133 performs as a styling aid/conditioner offering firm, flexible hold properties without the addition of plasticizing materials and can provide good sheen and softness.','Polycare 133; Poly[[3-(2-methylpropenamido)propyl]trimethylammoniumchloride]; Poly(acrylamide Trimethylammonium Chloride)','Keep container tightly closed. Store in a well-ventilated, cool area.','[\"463 lb. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Polymer\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9644,'POLYDEXTROSE','102498','GCC','68424-04-4','1','polydextrose','White to cream fine powder',NULL,'Is a reduced-calorie bulking agent, that can partially replace sugars and in some cases fats in reduced-calorie foods. It also functions s a bodying agent and humectant. Applications include desserts, specific baked goods, frozen dairy desserts, chewing gum, and candy.','Polydextrose; Unoxy P; Litesse Powder; Poly-D-glucose; Polydextrose solution; Polydextrose, Untreated, FCC','Store in a cool, dry, well ventilated place and out of direct sunlight. Store away from sources of heat or ignition. Store away from incompatible materials','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"50 lb. Bag\",\"50 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"25 kg. Poly Bag\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"100 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Food & bev.\"]','[\"Bodying agent\"]','C12H22O11','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\"