ow viscous liquid with a faint odor',NULL,'Is an emulsifier in self-emulsifying oil formulations with elevated water level. It is a PEG-free refatting agent especially for the use in body washes,liquid soaps, bath oils, and wet wipes.','Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate; Polyglycerol-4-caprate; Tegosoft PC 41','Store in cool, dry conditions at a temperature between 15øC (59øF).','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"25 kg. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emulsifier\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48580 S 3 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9662,'POLYGLYCERYL-4 DIISOSTEARATE/POLYHYDROXYSTEARATE/SEBACATE','102545','GCC','849230-52-0','1','polyglyceryl-4-diisostearatepolyhydroxystearateseb','Dark yellow liquid with characteristic odor',NULL,'It has excellent emulsion stabilization propertieseven at low concentrations. It is used in low viscosity W/O lotions with a very light feeling on the skin. It also allows the formulation of W/O lotions with a very low content of the oil phase providing a pleasant , non- oily feeling on the skin.','Polyglyceryl-4 Diisostearate/Polyhydroxystearate/Sebacate; Isolan GPS','Keep in sealed, unopened, original containers at 60ø – 80ø F. Avoid conditions of high humidity and temperature.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 kg. Open HD Pail\",\"25 kg. Bag\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emulsifiers\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:56','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9663,'POLYGLYCERYL-4 ISOSTEARATE','102546','GCC','63705-03-3','1','polyg