',NULL,'Carnosic acid is a kind of naturally occurring phenolic compound with antioxidant properties. It is considered to be a high effect, natural and oil-soluble antioxidant. The medical research indicates that, it can eliminate the free radicals that over-produced by the body and annihilate the singlet oxygen to protect the structure of the cell membrane, which can lead to slow down the aging process. In addition; it can stimulate and accelerate the metabolism of the fat by anti-oxidant activity. Not only can it lower the blood pressure, but it can also promote the lipid compounds to emit from the manure so as to lose weight. It is used in cometics for its anti-aging properties.','Rosemary Ext 30% Carnoic Powder; Salvin; Carnosic acid from Rosmarinus officinalis; Deoxypicrosalvinic Acid','Store at -20øC.','[\"25 Gram Poly Bag\",\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\",\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Botanicals\",\"antioxidants\"]','C20H28O4','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: N\\/A\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 274.2 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 190 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: 332.43 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9921,'ROSEMARY EXT 3% ROSMARINIC PWD','102857','GCC','20283-92-5','1','rosemary-ext-3-rosmarinic-pwd','Red-orange powder',NULL,'Rosmarinic acid is a caffeic acid ester found in a variety of plants. It has antioxidant and/or medicinal properties. Rosmarinic acid is a potential anxiolytic as it acts as a GABA transaminase inhibitor, more specifically on 4-aminobutyrate transaminase. Rosmarinic acid also inhibits the expression of indoleamine 2,3-dioxygenase via its cyclooxygenase-inhibiting properties.','Rosemary Ext 3% Rosmarinic Powder; Rosmarinate; 4-dihydroxy-; Rosemary Acid; Labiatenic Acid','Store at room temperature.','[\"50 Gram Poly Bag\",\"100 Gram HDP