al, antiseptic, and enhances the activity of preservatives.','Salicylic Acid USP CR 200 Mesh; Salicylic Acid Technical Grade; Unichem Salac; 2-Hydroxybenzoic acid; 2-Carboxyphenol; Salicylic acid','Keep away from sources of ignition. Do not store in direct sunlight. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area away from incompatible substances. Store protected from moisture.','[\"50 Gram Bottle\",\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"100 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Preservatives\\/antimicrobials\"]','C7H6O3','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 157 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 158-161 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 138.12 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(9938,'SALICYLIC ACID USP CRYSTAL','102874','GCC','69-72-7','1','salicylic-acid-usp-crystal','White odorless crystals',NULL,'Is a beta-hydroxyacid with keratolytic and anti-inflammatory activity. It helps dissolve the top layer of corneum cells, improving the look and feel of the skin. Salicylic acid is an effective ingredient in acne productsand as such is widely used in acne soaps and lotions. Because it is lipid soluble it can more easily reduce sebaceous follicle bloackage by penetrating the pores and exfoliating the cellular buildup. It is antimicrobial, antiseptic, and enhances the activity of preservatives.','Salicylic Acid USP Crystal; Salicylic Acid USP CR 200 Mesh; Salicylic Acid Technical Grade; Unichem Salac; 2-Hydroxybenzoic acid; 2-Carboxyphenol; Salicylic acid','Keep away from sources of ignition. Do not store in direct sunlight. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area away from incompatible substances. Store protected from moisture.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 lb. Bottle\",\"250 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Preservatives\\/antimicrobi