aging & anti-wrinkle products, pre/after sun lotions, protecting / nourishing & moisturizing skin care products, treatments for sensitive, dry skin.Sodium hyaluronate has been utilized in ophthalmic medical device (used for surgery of cataract), drug for arthritis (injection), eye drops, and topical uses. It is also used in cosmetic products such as hydrating gels, moisturizing creams & lotions, anti-aging & anti-wrinkle products, pre/after sun lotions, protecting / nourishing & moisturizing skin care products, treatments for sensitive, dry skin.','Sodium Hyaluronate 95% LMW P K; Sodium Hyaluronate 95% Powder; Healon; Hyaluronic acid sodium salt from bovine vitreous humor','Store in cool dry place, protect from light.','[\"2 Gram Poly Bag\",\"5 Gram Poly Bag\",\"10 Gram Bag\",\"25 Gram Bottle\",\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"500 Gram Foil Bag\",\"2 kg. Bottle\",\"5 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Intermediates\",\"moisturizer\",\"surfactants\"]','C14H22NNaO11','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 432.5 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: 241-247 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 403.31 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10116,'SODIUM HYDROXIDE 10% SOLUTION','103095','GCC','1310-73-2, Mixture','1','sodium-hydroxide-10-solution','Clear colorless odorless liquid',NULL,'Sodium hydroxide is a popular strong base used in industry. Sodium hydroxide is also used in the manufacture of sodium salts and detergents, pH regulation, and organic synthesis. It is used in the Bayer process of aluminium production. Sodium hydroxide is also widely used in pulping of wood for making paper or regenerated fibers. In a similar fashion, sodium hydroxide is used to digest tissues, such as in a process that was used with farm animals at one time. Sodium hydroxide is frequently used as an industrial cleaning agent where it is often called \"caustic\".','Sodium Hydroxide 10% Solution; Lye; Caustic soda; Sodium hydrate; Soda lye','Store in a tightly closed container. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area away from incompatible substances. Keep away from metals.','[\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"Industrial\"]','[\"Surfactants\",\"chemicals general\"]','NaOH','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 3 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 48580 SUB 3 CLASS 55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 9-10 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 39.99 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10117,'SODIUM HYDROXIDE 20% SOLUTION','103096','GCC','1310-73-2, 7732-18-5','1','sodium-hydroxide-20-solution','Clear liquid',NULL,'Sodium hydroxide is a popular strong base used in industry. Sodium hydroxide is also used in the manufacture of sodium salts and detergents, pH regulation, and organic synthesis. It is used in the Bayer process of aluminium production. Sodium hydroxide is also widely used in pulping of wood for making paper or regenerated fibers. In a similar fashion, sodium hydroxide is used to digest tissues, such as in a process that was used with farm animals at one time. Sodium hydroxide is frequently used as an industrial cleaning agent where it is often called \"caustic\".','Sodium Hydroxide 20% Solution; Unichem SOHY20; Lye; Caustic soda; Sodium hydrate; Soda lye','Store in a tightly closed container. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area away from incompatible substances. Keep away from metals.','[null]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"industrial\"]','[\"Surfactants\",\"chemicals general\"]','NaOH','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 3 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 46230 SUB3 CLASS 55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 9-10 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: