d antipyretic. Sodium salicylate also acts as non-steroidal anti-inflammatory drug and induces apoptosis in cancer cells and also necrosis. It is also a potential replacement for aspirin for people sensitive to it. It may also be used as a phosphor for the detection of vacuum ultraviolet radiation and electrons.','Sodium Salicylate USP Crystal; 2-hydroxy-benzoicacimonosodiumsalt; NASAL; Benzoicacid,2-hydroxy-,monosodiumsalt; Diuretin','Keep containers tightly closed in a dry, cool and well-ventilated place. Protect from light and strong oxidizing agents.','[\"50 Gram Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 lb. HDPE OH Pail\",\"25 kg. Bag\",\"25 kg. Box\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Acidulants\"]','C7H5NaO3','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 3 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 48580 SUB 3 CLASS 55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: >300 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 160.10 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10201,'SODIUM SELENATE 98% ANHYDROUS','103230','GCC','13410-01-0','1','sodium-selenate-98-anhydrous','Odorless white to off-white powder',NULL,'Sodium selenate is a common ingredient in some insecticides used against mites, aphids, and mealybugs. It is chosen for its selenium content and high solubility, sodium selenate is a common ingredient in over-the-counter vitamin supplements. Seleneium is a trace essential element. Sodium selenate and selenite are also common in premix animal feed.','Sodium Selenate 98% Anhydrous; Disodium selenate; Selenic acid, disodium salt; Natriumseleniat; Sodium selenate: (Disodium selenate)','Keep container tightly closed in a dry and well-ventilated place.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"50 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\",\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Nutritional supplements\",\"vitamins\"]','Na2O4Se','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 32oC\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 188.94 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10202,'SODIUM SELENITE POWDER TECH','103231','GCC','10102-18-8','1','sodium-selenite-powder-tech','White powder',NULL,'Selenium is an essential element, sodium selenite is an ingredient in some food supplements. The US Food and Drug Administration approved a selenium supplement to animal diets, however the most common form is sodium selenite for pet foods. It is also used together with the related barium and zinc selenites, sodium selenite is mainly used in the manufacture of colorless glass.','Sodium Selenite Powder Tech; Disodium selenite; Sodium selenite, 44-46% Se, anhydrous; Natriumselenit; Sodium selenite, anhydrous','Store in a cool, dry place. Keep container closed when not in use.','[\"50 Gram Bottle\",\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"100 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\",\"Industrial\"]','[\"Nutritional supplements\",\"vitamins\"]','Na2O3Se','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 350 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: 172.94 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10203,'SODIUM SESQUICARBONATE','103232','GCC','533-96-0','1','sodium-sesquicarbonate','White crystalline needles',NULL,'Sodium sesquicarbonate is used in bath salts, swimming pools, as an alkalinity source for water treatment, and as a phosphate free trisodium phosphate replacement for heavy duty cleaning. Sodium sesquicarbonate is also used in the conservation of copper and copper alloy artefacts that corrode due to contact with salt (called \"bronze disease\" due to its effect on bronze). It is also used as a precipitating water softener, which combines with hard water minerals (calcium- and magnesium-based minerals) to form an insoluble precipitate, removing these hardness minerals from the water.','Sodium Sesquicarbonate; Carbonicacid, sodium salt (2:3); Sodium Carbonate, Sesquioxide; Kanwa','Protect from excessive heat and moisture. Store away from acids.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"50 lb. Bag\",\"50 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"100 lb. Bag\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\",\"Industrial\"]','[\"Chemicals general\",\"acidulants\"]','C2HNa3O6','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: N\\/A\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC48581 S 0 CL55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 190.00 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10204,'SODIUM SILICATE N SOL\'N 40 DE','103234','GCC','1344-09-8','1','sodium-silicate-n-soln-40-de','Viscous liquid',NULL,'It is often used in metal cleaning, textile processing, laundering and de-inking paper, to washing dishes, dairy equipment, bottles, floors, and locomotives.','Sodium Silicate N Solution 40 DE; Liquid sodium silicate; Water glass; Sodium silicate liquid siliceous','Keep container tightly closed. Do not store in aluminum container or use aluminum fittings or transfer lines, as flammable hydrogen gas may be generated. Keep separated from incompatible substances','[\"50 lb. Pail\",\"635 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Industrial\"]','[\"Chemicals general\"]','Na2O3Si','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NON REGULATED CHEMICALS NOI CLASS 55\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 1410 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 122.06 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10205,'SODIUM SILICATE SOLUTION E','103235','GCC','1344-09-8','1','sodium-silicate-sol