ter/DME).','Solubilisant LRI','Store in cool, dry, well-ventilated area in a tightly closed container.','[\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Surfactants\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: > 100 \\u00f8C\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10268,'SOLUVIT RICHTER','103300','GCC','NA','1','soluvit-richter','Clear yellow liquid',NULL,'It is a multivitamin herbal complex. A non-inonic surfactant is used for solubilization of a horse chestnut extract, vitamins A, E, F, H (Biotin) and vitamins of the B group in an aqueous-alcoholic medium. It is recommended for use in aqueous and aqueous-alcoholic vitamin preparations for skin and hair (including bath and shampoo preparations) designed for oily, but also dry and rough skin and scalps. Further it can be used for skin and scalps poorly supplied with blood, and for dry and greasy hair.','Soluvit Richter; Unitichter; N’-(ethylcarbonimidoyl)-N,N-dimethylpropane-1,3-diamine','Store away from direct sunlight.','[\"1 kg. Bottle\",\"25 kg. Poly Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Surfactants\",\"vitamins\",\"nutritional supplements\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: N\\/A\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10269,'SOLVENT DE (CARBOTONE)','103301','GCC','111-90-0','1','solvent-de-carbotone','Clear, colorless, hygroscopic liquid',NULL,'It is an industrial solvent.','Solvent DE (Carbotone); 2-(2-Ethoxyethoxy)ethanol; 3,6-dioxa-1-octanol, DEGEE, diethylene ; Dowanal DE','Keep away from sources of ignition. Store in a tightly closed container. Stor