at and reduces separation.','Soy Lecithin, Powdered; Ultralec P; Soybean Lecithin; Phosphatidylcholine','Store in a tightly closed container. Store in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area away from incompatible substances. Store protected from moisture.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"44 lb. Box\",\"44 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Food & bev.\"]','[\"Flavors\",\"vegetable oils\",\"Surfactants\",\"Emulsifiers\"]','C36H23N8Na3O11S3','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: 908.78 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10313,'SOY PHOSPHOLIPIDS (PHOSPHATIDES)','103359','GCC','8008-43-5','1','soy-phospholipids-phosphatides','Amber to brownish viscous material',NULL,'Alcolec BS is a high grade, unmodified fluid Lecithin. It contains a high level of natural, functional phospholipids. Alcolec BS conforms to the food chemicals codex.','Soy Phospholipids (Phosphatides); T/N: Alcolec BS “OU”; Single Bleached Lecethin Fluid; Soy Phospholipid; Unolex BS','Storage temperature should be between 60§ to 90§ F (16§ to 32§ C).','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"44 lb. Pail\",\"450 lb. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Food & bev.\"]','[\"Fatty acids\",\"vegetable oils\",\"phosphates\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 1\\/2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: >400\\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10314,'SOY PROTEIN ISOLATE','103360','GCC','9010-10-0','1','soy-protein-isolate','Light yellow powder',NULL,'Soy isolates are mainly used to improve the texture of meat products, but are also used to increase protein content, to enhance moisture retention, and as an emulsifier. Pure soy protein isolate is used mainly by the food industry. It is sometimes available in health stores or in the pharmacy section of the supermarket. It is usually found combined with other food ingredients.','Soy Protein Isolate; Unipro 710; Supro 710; Soy protein concentrate; Soybean protein','Store in a cool dry area away from other incompatible materials.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 kg. HDPE OH Pail\",\"44 lb. Box\",\"44 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Food & bev.\"]','[\"Emulsifiers\",\"nutritional supplements\",\"proteins\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10315,'SPEARMINT OIL 80%','103361','GCC','8008-79-5','1','spearmint-oil-80','Light yellow to greenish-yellow clear liquid',NULL,'Is a cooling, aromatic stimulant described as having cleansing and decongesting properties. It is indicated for acne and oily skin. Its fragrance and therapeutic activity is similar to that of peppermint but fresher and less harsh.','Spearmint Oil 80%; Mentha; Spicata; Crispmint Oil; Curled Mint Oil','Store in tightly sealed containers and kept in a dry, well-ventilated space. Keep containers upright to prevent spills/leakage.','[\"100 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"10 lb. Pail\",\"25 lb. Steel Pail\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Essential oils\"]','C6H14O6','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 70 RV 2.15\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: 160 \\u00f8F\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 182.17 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:3