e becomes ineffective over time, while stannous fluoride remains effective in strengthening tooth enamel.','Stannous Fluoride USP; tin (2+) fluoride, stannous fluoride, tin difluoride; Tin(II) fluoride','Keep container tightly sealed.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"5 kg. HDPE WM Bottle\",\"25 kg. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Surfactants\"]','SnF2','[\"Origin: Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 60000 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 215 \\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: 156.69 g\\/mol\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10328,'STARCH 1500','103374','GCC','9005-25-8','1','starch-1500','White powder',NULL,'It is used in the pharmaceutical industry as a tablet/capsule diluent and as a tablet disintegrant.','Starch 1500; Unistar 15; alpha-starch; amylomaizevii; Clearjel; claro5591','Keep container tightly closed in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area. Store away from incompatible materials.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Excipients\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Synthetic\",\"Shelf life: 2 years from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 S 2 CL 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: 256-258\\u00f8C\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: YES\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:57','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10329,'STARCH 1551','103375','GCC','9005-25-8','1','starch-1551','White powder',NULL,'It is used in the pharmaceutical industry as a tablet binder.','Starch 1551; National 78-1551; Pregelatinized Corn Starch; Meluna; Trogum; Strke','Keep container tightly closed in a cool, dry, well-ventilated area. Store away from incompatible materials.','[\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"80 lb. Bag\",\"80 lb. Fiber Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Pharmaceutical\"]','[\"Binders\"]','N/A','[\"Origin: Vegetable\\/Syn