ntainer tightly closed in a cool, dry and well-ventilated place.','[\"250 ml. HDPE Bottle\",\"36 lb. Pail\",\"190 kg. Poly Drum\",\"429 lb. Stel Drum\",\"200 kg. Steel Drum\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Cosmetics\"]','[\"Emollient & esters\",\"antioxidants\",\"vitamins\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Natural\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:58','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10600,'WHEAT PROTEIN ISOLATE PROLITE','103679','GCC','8002-80-0','1','wheat-protein-isolate-prolite','Tan to light cream color powder',NULL,'Its softer texture and lower molecular weight allow for a unique flavor and textural advantage in traditional or better-for-you applications. It forms an elastic dough in water, but is not as functional as vital wheat gluten, making Prolite 200 a unique textural enhancement to cakes, cookies, brownies and whole-grain products.','Wheat Protein Isolate – Prolite 200 Food Grade; Smartbind wheat protein isolate; Triticum aestivum protein isolate','Keep container tightly closed in a cool, dry and well-ventilated place.','[\"100 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"250 Gram HDPE WM Bottle\",\"30 lb. Bag\",\"1 lb. Bulk\"]','[\"Food & bev.\"]','[\"Food additive\",\"lactate & lactic acid\"]',NULL,'[\"Origin: Natural\",\"Shelf life: 1 year from mfg. date\",\"Freight Classification: NMFC 43940 SUB 2 CLASS 85\",\"Kosher Status: Not Kosher\",\"Flash Point: N\\/A\",\"Melting Point: N\\/A\",\"API: NO\",\"Allergen: NO\",\"Hazmat: NO\",\"Molecular Weight: N\\/A\"]','2025-04-10 07:11:58','2025-08-04 14:56:33'),(10601,'WHITE WILLOW BARK EXTRACT','103680','GCC','84082-82-6','1','white-willow-bark-extract','Yellowish brown powder',NULL,'It is a deodorant with tonic and astringent properties. It is used effectively in products for acne and eczema.','White Willow Bark Extract; Extract of wi